，直接给你可验收进度。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04b76fdf640436710169b7559942d881a0b738b7dc28ae8730\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_AIMS0c9sdaLLGCsyn2RmlEoR|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75599b6f081a093b487168ba1ffa3","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/news-market/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/news-market/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2177,"output":199,"cacheRead":22016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773622676222}}
{"type":"message","id":"814b15aa","parentId":"e489db78","timestamp":"2026-03-16T00:58:02.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_AIMS0c9sdaLLGCsyn2RmlEoR|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75599b6f081a093b487168ba1ffa3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: news-market\ndescription: 全球股市早间要闻生成技能。用于每天早上生成包含全球股市相关新闻、大盘体温、板块映射、看涨/看跌判断的早间报告。触发场景：(1) 每天08:50定时执行 (2) 用户手动触发\"生成早间要闻\"或\"今日股市消息\"\n---\n\n# News Market - 全球股市早间要闻\n\n## Overview\n\n生成每日全球股市早间要闻报告，包含：\n- 全球股市相关新闻摘要\n- A股大盘体温（涨跌停、成交量、情绪指标）\n- 板块涨跌热力图\n- 看涨/看跌判断及操作建议\n\n## 使用方式\n\n### 手动触发\n用户发送以下指令时执行：\n- \"生成早间要闻\"\n- \"今日股市消息\"\n- \"全球股市早餐\"\n\n### 定时任务\n每天 08:50 自动执行（需配置 cron）\n\n## 数据来源\n\n1. **A股数据**：AkShare / 腾讯财经\n2. **港股数据**：AkShare\n3. **美股数据**：yfinance\n4. **新闻资讯**：东方财富网、同花顺\n\n## 输出格式\n\n生成结构化报告，包含：\n1. 📈 **全球市场概览** - 各主要市场涨跌幅\n2. 🇨🇳 **A股大盘体温** - 涨跌停数量、成交量、情绪评分\n3. 🔥 **板块热力图** - 涨幅前5/跌幅前5\n4. 🎯 **判断与建议** - 看涨/看跌、仓位建议\n\n## 脚本执行\n\n```bash\n# 在 workspace 根目录生成 markdown + json\npython3 skills/news-market/scripts/generate_morning_news_free.py \\\n  --output research/reports/global_market_morning_free_$(date +%Y%m%d).md \\\n  --json-output research/reports/global_market_morning_free_$(date +%Y%m%d).json\n\n# 生成并推送到飞书（按 config.json）\npython3 skills/news-market/scripts/run_and_push_morning_news.py\n\n# 安装 08:50 自动调度（工作日 + 交易日过滤）\nbash skills/news-market/scripts/install_cron_0850.sh\n```\n\n## 配置项\n\n- `skills/news-market/config.json`\n  - `output_dir`: 报告输出目录\n  - `report_prefix`: 报告前缀\n  - `feishu.target_user`: 飞书 DM 目标\n  - `schedule.cron`: 默认 cron 表达式（08:50 工作日）\n  - `schedule.trading_day_only`: 是否仅交易日推送\n- `scripts/config.py`\n  - `REPORT_TIME`: 报告生成时间\n  - `MARKETS`: 关注的市场列表\n  - `SECTOR_COUNT`: 板块显示数量\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773622682485}}
