sing the current app to add functionality for loading model files from app assets. However, I need to confirm whether those assets actually exist first. To do that, I should inspect the relevant files within the app. This is a crucial step to ensure we can effectively implement the new functionality without running into issues later on. Let's move forward and check what's available!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我现在开始干，先把 **能交付 APK 的阻断** 摊平：查模型资产、语音链路默认配置、然后直接改代码并重打包。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04b76fdf640436710169b75b9d03a881a095f74cabb0ba7ac0\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebB1HwGJ8zng0t8gZvOxgVeb|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75b9d162c81a092d6708944ce2717","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app\nprintf '=== sherpa refs in source ===\\n'\ngrep -Rni \"sherpa\" app/src/main/java app/src/main/assets app/build.gradle.kts docs 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,220p'\nprintf '\\n=== model-like files in repo ===\\n'\nfind . \\( -iname '*.onnx' -o -iname 'tokens.txt' -o -iname '*.aar' \\) | sed -n '1,220p'\nprintf '\\n=== current build debug compile ===\\n'\n./gradlew :app:compileDebugKotlin --console=plain","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"set -e\\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app\\nprintf '=== sherpa refs in source ===\\\\n'\\ngrep -Rni \\\"sherpa\\\" app/src/main/java app/src/main/assets app/build.gradle.kts docs 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,220p'\\nprintf '\\\\n=== model-like files in repo ===\\\\n'\\nfind . \\\\( -iname '*.onnx' -o -iname 'tokens.txt' -o -iname '*.aar' \\\\) | sed -n '1,220p'\\nprintf '\\\\n=== current build debug compile ===\\\\n'\\n./gradlew :app:compileDebugKotlin --console=plain\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app\",\"yieldMs\":1000,\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage"