\"**Evaluating improvements**\\n\\nI'm considering how to improve functionality, possibly by using a factory fallback and adjusting app settings for auto-selection to enhance effectiveness. I should also search for strings like “离线预备” to see what comes up. Implementing an auto-seed for assets could also help. Additionally, I need to inspect the UI selection callback, particularly around line 520, as that might reveal some issues or areas for enhancement. Let's keep this organized!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_400U0A8yEQNmUXhE7FKwUsVn|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75c076a1881a0920f7f7135d3f908","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt","offset":500,"limit":220},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt\",\"offset\":500,\"limit\":220}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2721,"output":112,"cacheRead":104192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773624322217}}
{"type":"message","id":"83751e58","parentId":"ab9c2058","timestamp":"2026-03-16T01:25:28.188Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_400U0A8yEQNmUXhE7FKwUsVn|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75c076a1881a0920f7f7135d3f908","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            )\n\n            \"home\" -> HomeScreen(\n                currentBookTitle = currentBookTitle,\n                promptLanguage = promptLanguage,\n                totalStars = progressRepository.totalStars(currentBookId),\n                currentStreak = progressRepository.currentStreak(),\n                longestStreak = progressRepository.longestStreak(),\n                practiceProgress = progressRepository.practiceProgress(currentBookId),\n                badgeCount = progressRepository.getUnlockedBadges().size,\n                errorMessage = errorMessage,\n                wrongCount = progressRepository.wrongCount(currentBookId, questionBank),\n                onChangeBook = { screen = \"book_select\" },\n                onStartWordQuiz = { chooseMode(QuizMode.WORD) },\n                onStartSentenceQuiz = { chooseMode(QuizMode.SENTENCE) },\n                onStartMixedQuiz = { chooseMode(QuizMode.MIXED) },\n                onStartWrongReview = { startWrongReview() },\n                onOpenSettings = { screen = \"settings\" },\n                onViewBadges = { screen = \"badges\" },\n            )\n\n            \"settings\" -> SettingsScreen(\n                promptLanguage = promptLanguage,\n                autoSpeakEnglish = autoSpeakEnglish,\n                asrEngineMode = asrEngineMode,\n                sherpaEnabled = sherpaEnabled,\n                sherpaModelStatus = sherpaModelStatus,\n                ttsReady = speechSpeaker.isReady(),\n                ttsStatusMessage = speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage(),\n                bundledSpeechBuiltIn = speechSpeaker.hasBundledAudio(),\n                onSelectPromptLanguage = { promptLanguageName = it.name },\n                onToggleAutoSpeak = {\n                    autoSpeakEnglish = !autoSpeakEnglish\n                    settingsRepository.setAutoSpeakEnglish(autoSpeakEnglish)\n                    if (autoSpeakEnglish && !speechSpeaker.isReady() && speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage() != \"语音引擎初始化中\") {\n                        errorMessage = speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage()\n                    } else if (!autoSpeakEnglish) {\n                        errorMessage = null\n                    }\n                },\n                onSelectAsrEngine = { mode ->\n                    asrEngineModeName = mode.name\n                    settingsRepository.setAsrEngineMode(mode)\n                    if (mode == AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX && !sherpaEnabled) {\n                        sherpaEnabled = true\n                        settingsRepository.setSherpaOnnxEnabled(true)\n                    }\n                    errorMessage = null\n                },\n                onOpenTtsSetup = {\n                    runCatching {\n                        openTtsSetup(context)\n                    }.onSuccess { opened ->\n                        errorMessage = if (opened) null else \"当前设备没有可用的系统语音设置入口\"\n                    }.onFailure {\n                        errorMessage = \"当前设备没有可用的系统语音设置入口\"\n                    }\n                },\n                onBack = { screen = \"home\" },\n            )\n\n            \"badges\" -> BadgesScreen(\n                allBadges = com.openclaw.englishworkbook.model.Badges.ALL,\n                unlockedBadges = progressRepository.getUnlockedBadges(),\n                currentStreak = progressRepository.currentStreak(),\n                longestStreak = progressRepository.longestStreak(),\n                onBack = { screen = \"home\" },\n            )\n\n            \"unit_select\" -> UnitSelectionScreen(\n                bookTitle = currentBookTitle,\n                mode = currentMode,\n                units = repository.availableUnits(currentBookId, currentMode),\n                totalCount = repository.questionCount(currentBookId, currentMode, null),\n                onSelectAll = { startQuiz(currentMode, null, \"全册混合\") },\n                onSelectUnit = { unitInfo -> startQuiz(currentMode, unitInfo.order, \"Unit ${unitInfo.order} · ${unitInfo.title}\") },\n                questionCountForUnit = { unitOrder -> repository.questionCount(currentBookId, currentMode, unitOrder) },\n                progressForUnit = { unitOrder -> progressRepository.unitProgress(currentBookId, currentMode, unitOrder) },\n                wrongCountForUnit = { unitOrder -> progressRepository.wrongCountForUnit(currentBookId, questionBank, unitOrder) },\n                masteryStarsForUnit = { unitOrder -> progressRepository.unitMasteryStars(currentBookId, unitOrder) },\n                onBack = { screen = \"home\" },\n            )\n\n            \"quiz\" -> {\n                val question = questions.getOrNull(currentIndex)\n                if (question == null) {\n                    ResultScreen(\n                        bookTitle = currentBookTitle,\n                        mode = currentMode,\n                        unitTitle = currentUnitTitle,\n                        result = SessionResult(total = questions.size, correct = correctCount),\n                        sessionWrongCount = sessionWrongIds.size,\n                        gainedStars = lastGainedStars,\n                        practiceBonusStars = practiceBonusStars,\n                        totalStars = maxOf(lastTotalStars, progressRepository.totalStars(currentBookId)),\n                        totalWrongCount = progressRepository.wrongCount(currentBookId, questionBank),\n                        newBadges = newBadges + practiceRewardBadges,\n                        onBackHome = { backToHome() },\n                        onRetry = { if (currentMode == QuizMode.WRONG_REVIEW) startWrongReview() else startQuiz(currentMode, currentUnit, currentUnitTitle) },\n                        onChooseUnit = { if (currentMode == QuizMode.WRONG_REVIEW) screen = \"home\" else screen = \"unit_select\" },\n                    )\n                } else {\n                    QuizScreen(\n                        bookTitle = currentBookTitle,\n                        mode = currentMode,\n                        unitTitle = currentUnitTitle,\n                        question = question,\n                        promptLanguage = promptLanguage,\n                        index = currentIndex + 1,\n                        total = questions.size,\n                        correctCount = correctCount,\n                        selectedAnswer = selectedAnswer,\n                        answered = answered,\n                        hintMessage = errorMessage,\n                        practiceAvailable = speechPracticeRecognizer.isAvailable(),\n                        practiceListening = speechPracticeRecognizer.isListening,\n                        practiceStatusMessage = speechPracticeRecognizer.statusMessage,\n                        practiceResult = speechPracticeRecognizer.lastResult,\n                        practiceRewardMessage = practiceRewardMessage,\n                        practiceRewardDetails = practiceRewardDetails,\n                        practiceRewardBadges = practiceRewardBadges,\n                        repairedWordsMessage = repairedWordsMessage,\n                        sentenceRetryLabel = sentenceRetryLabel,\n                        onRetrySentencePractice = if (!sentenceRetryText.isNullOrBlank() && !sentenceRetryLabel.isNullOrBlank() && !sentenceRetryRewardId.isNullOrBlank()) {\n                            {\n                                val retryText = sentenceRetryText!!\n                                val retryLabelValue = sentenceRetryLabel!!\n                                val retryRewardId = sentenceRetryRewardId!!\n                                repairedWordsMessage = null\n                                sentenceRetryText = null\n                                sentenceRetryLabel = null\n                                sentenceRetryRewardId = null\n                                sentenceRetryInProgress = true\n                                startReadAlong(retryText, retryLabelValue, retryRewardId)\n                            }\n                        } else null,\n                        onSpeakPrompt = {\n                            if (!speechSpeaker.speak(question.promptEn)) {\n                                val status = speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage()\n                                errorMessage = if (status == \"语音引擎初始化中\") null else status\n                            } else {\n                                errorMessage = null\n                            }\n                        },\n                        onPracticePrompt = {\n                            activeSentencePracticeText = question.promptEn\n                            activeSentencePracticeLabel = \"题目跟读\"\n                            activeSentencePracticeRewardId = \"${question.id}:prompt\"\n                            sentenceRetryText = null\n                            sentenceRetryLabel = null\n                            sentenceRetryRewardId = null\n                            repairedWordsMessage = null\n                            repairedWordsSnapshot = emptyList()\n                            sentenceRetryInProgress = false\n                            startReadAlong(question.promptEn, \"题目跟读\", \"${question.id}:prompt\")\n                        },\n                        onSpeakAnswer = {\n                            val ans = question.answerEn\n                            if (!speechSpeaker.speak(ans)) {\n                                val status = speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage()\n                                errorMessage = if (status == \"语音引擎初始化中\") null else status\n                            } else {\n                                errorMessage = null\n                            }\n                        },\n                        onPracticeAnswer = {\n                            activeSentencePracticeText = question.answerEn\n                            activeSentencePracticeLabel = \"答案跟读\"\n                            activeSentencePracticeRewardId = \"${question.id}:answer\"\n                            sentenceRetryText = null\n                            sentenceRetryLabel = null\n                            sentenceRetryRewardId = null\n                            repairedWordsMessage = null\n                            repairedWordsSnapshot = emptyList()\n                            sentenceRetryInProgress = false\n                            startReadAlong(question.answerEn, \"答案跟读\", \"${question.id}:answer\")\n                        },\n                        onSpeakWord = { word ->\n                            if (!speechSpeaker.speak(word)) {\n                                val status = speechSpeaker.getStatusMessage()\n                                errorMessage = if (status == \"语音引擎初始化中\") null else status\n                            } else {\n                                errorMessage = null\n                            }\n                        },\n                        onPracticeWord = { word ->\n                            repairedWordsSnapshot = speechPracticeRecognizer.lastResult?.score?.targetWordFeedback.orEmpty()\n                                .filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\n                                .map { it.word }\n                            startReadAlong(word, \"逐词跟读\", \"${question.id}:word:$word\")\n                        },\n                        onAnswer = { option ->\n                            if (!answered) {\n                                selectedAnswer = option\n                                answered = true\n                                val expected = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.ZH) question.answerEn else question.answerZh\n                                if (option == expected) {\n                                    correctCount += 1\n                                    sessionWrongIds = sessionWrongIds - question.id\n                                } else {\n                                    sessionWrongIds = sessionWrongIds + question.id\n                                }\n                            }\n                        },\n                        onNext = {\n                            speechPracticeRecognizer.reset()\n                            selectedAnswer = null\n                            answered = false\n                            if (currentIndex >= questions.lastIndex) {\n                                progressRepository.recordQuizResult(currentBookId, currentMode, currentUnit, questions, sessionWrongIds)\n                                val reward = progressRepository.applyReward(\n                                    bookId = currentBookId,\n                                    mode = currentMode,\n                                    unit = currentUnit,\n                                    accuracy = if (questions.isEmpty()) 0 else (correctCount * 100) / questions.size,\n                                )\n                                lastGainedStars = reward.gainedStars\n                                lastTotalStars = reward.totalStars\n                                newBadges = reward.newBadges\n                                if (reward.gainedStars > 0 || reward.newBadges.isNotEmpty()) {\n\n[846 more lines in file. Use offset=720 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773624328174}}
{"type":"message","id":"5eb2229e","parentId":"83751e58","timestamp":"2026-03-16T01:25:54.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring speech practice options**\n\nI'm considering encoding this in a status message. It might be a good idea to create a FallbackSpeechPracticeEngine. To do this simply, I could modify the factory so it returns a new ResilientSpeechPracticeEngine wrapper. This wrapper would accommodate either the system or sherpa while also prefixing the status. It seems like a clean solution that could enhance functionality. I wonder if this approach will work smoothly when implemented.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_04b76fdf640436710169b75c0c1ab481a09b9a4fc5d09288c9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpt1wgyxlNYIqb2zw3ld3ml5_fbRF8BzS1lXtlcs33UlFmj5B6RTG_oWGS7MmrEHBEsfMEgy0-a7-_1MI6vfd-dQK-IthuwtIYr_0BM4wIq2hnnCM_shu9lSMyiNzAkREg_vYydG6psnpfVIRcEmD6pLPtkROt1PlQpDE-oDautPjnQUEPn5M1YWRMzWU5H56f70Gh_JRPbLMTFzzh8358hFOl5sYxyNLBoIjBnA3oNESqrY6jpToP8G32N1H6gMQIEKLAXI0aqcn-PpeDvra32bzJV5dbQ243kLo-3F3mEvJUXGVIgifre7KPUhu4l1YPDute75SAg2kRV-VvnyQ4E6UQfM0aA55D490280fnU5zt3yP1pjpgEgBiqTJ8qAmTc3vthjVqFD6LQY-l7QKUk2JowzcBLQd5uogwccngr43bcDNjzHqIeXlP51Dd-cNVjYX9bzr3kxwfkO-nHlRzMYjNq_MBiT1XJojqKlslpo826xlOcUKJHj-r_RqHcHS2fcwiplLAkgGxUSLnH6jnvYOacVc_xffYgxzz9-w7jTHdY09VPHDesgUiz_ooOoP7I52xQj65tmIdZq99ZC5kfcfkqoyZ10uyWqNmUcbziTdLvudK4wFQ4NPyDUjuq-niOqdAKiQ8OIsUzMeReMGjq2D_PDEBI7z4WGgfwP7MURfxFdNIyYh03_WU6K9cUlzPFf9Ew3j9OLLfJjImIJp86dzP85_719I29Oa0OcCM1DO8Jpt8mNZONZS6GaxzYR-htnfU3WAO79KgExk3Faw4J8OjNFThah1NOWsAmhwNWZv_fY9Do8lVmo30K1XenzAThPQV-5ShQ2IXPiOWT2g0EydRS61NMsyyJ9muLDqkSniDSvgvFVbh97E46AZHT43iQFoG1U7eGeGJsJpXY6MxiMYTdNF6Xj7hk-VxWby9U6-29zOrHOG_PjarnYMztLDf3Hq2nm8_YTJfhOmGMTemuyuXo6JUDGbIk74JJttmVLtK-wMVjPfg_3GCOmkc5kJIIgkXQ4TGHmGkmZqe6-DVpCakxBOR_U-OdQKP8LKokXjHmKLOtBBviPX6KZS_XputNh70ssi0TLV3YN15IexDOSsaCMcnx5nCVD26F3MY241ZseN9dcPqgFLIVuc8YfwdaKoYxjXGpYjaB4qWGh2AQvhnZlSpS_LwiqZQUCDlR2SToOi3wxerraG