{"type":"message","id":"557fc982","parentId":"5eb2229e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T01:25:54.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Qr3a6bIq6rE4IrOL5cA2Czcm|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75c20b03881a09b4d376114c76e32","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                    // Fill empty space if row has less than 3 items\n                    repeat(3 - rowBadges.size) {\n                        Spacer(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f))\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        OutlinedButton(onClick = onBack, modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().height(72.dp)) {\n            Text(\"返回首页\")\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun SettingsScreen(\n    promptLanguage: PromptLanguage,\n    autoSpeakEnglish: Boolean,\n    asrEngineMode: AsrEngineMode,\n    sherpaEnabled: Boolean,\n    sherpaModelStatus: SherpaOnnxModelStatus,\n    ttsReady: Boolean,\n    ttsStatusMessage: String,\n    bundledSpeechBuiltIn: Boolean,\n    onSelectPromptLanguage: (PromptLanguage) -> Unit,\n    onToggleAutoSpeak: () -> Unit,\n    onSelectAsrEngine: (AsrEngineMode) -> Unit,\n    onOpenTtsSetup: () -> Unit,\n    onBack: () -> Unit,\n) {\n    Column(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize().padding(36.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(20.dp)) {\n        Text(text = \"家长设置\", fontSize = 32.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)\n        Text(text = \"选择题目展示语言：\")\n        LargeActionButton(text = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.ZH) \"✓ 中文提示 → 选英文答案\" else \"中文提示 → 选英文答案\", subtitle = \"适合先看中文，再认英文\", onClick = { onSelectPromptLanguage(PromptLanguage.ZH) })\n        LargeActionButton(text = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.EN) \"✓ 英文提示 → 选中文答案\" else \"英文提示 → 选中文答案\", subtitle = \"适合先看英文，再判断中文意思\", onClick = { onSelectPromptLanguage(PromptLanguage.EN) })\n\n        Text(text = \"跟读识别引擎：\")\n        Card(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth()) {\n            Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)) {\n                Text(\n                    text = if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) \"当前引擎：系统语音识别\" else \"当前引擎：sherpa-onnx（离线预备）\",\n                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,\n                )\n                LargeActionButton(\n                    text = if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) \"✓ 系统语音识别\" else \"系统语音识别\",\n                    subtitle = \"沿用当前手机系统语音服务\",\n                    onClick = { onSelectAsrEngine(AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) },\n                )\n                LargeActionButton(\n                    text = if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX) \"✓ sherpa-onnx（离线预备）\" else \"sherpa-onnx（离线预备）\",\n                    subtitle = if (sherpaModelStatus.isReady) \"模型已就绪，可进入下一步接入\" else \"免费离线路线，后续将绕开系统语音\",\n                    onClick = { onSelectAsrEngine(AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX) },\n                )\n                Text(\n                    text = if (sherpaEnabled) \"sherpa 状态：已启用配置\" else \"sherpa 状态：未启用配置\",\n                    style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                )\n                Text(\n                    text = if (sherpaModelStatus.isReady) {\n                        \"模型状态：已就绪（${sherpaModelStatus.modelDirPath}）\"\n                    } else {\n                        \"模型状态：未就绪，缺少 ${sherpaModelStatus.missingFiles.joinToString(\", \")}\"\n                    },\n                    style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                    color = if (sherpaModelStatus.isReady) MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primary else MaterialTheme.colorScheme.error,\n                )\n                Text(\n                    text = \"模型目录：${sherpaModelStatus.modelDirPath}\",\n                    style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                    color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onSurfaceVariant,\n                )\n            }\n        }\n\n        Text(text = \"朗读设置：\")\n        Card(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth()) {\n            Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)) {\n                Text(text = if (ttsReady) \"语音状态：已就绪\" else \"语音状态：不可用\", fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)\n                Text(text = ttsStatusMessage, style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall)\n                if (!bundledSpeechBuiltIn && !ttsReady) {\n                    Text(\n                        text = \"当前版本未找到内置语音包，请检查媒体音量；必要时再进入系统语音设置作为备用方案。\",\n                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.error,\n                    )\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        LargeActionButton(\n            text = if (autoSpeakEnglish) \"✓ 自动朗读英文题目\" else \"自动朗读英文题目\",\n            subtitle = if (autoSpeakEnglish) \"每题自动播放英文朗读\" else \"需要手动点击播放按钮\",\n            onClick = onToggleAutoSpeak\n        )\n        if (!bundledSpeechBuiltIn) {\n            OutlinedButton(onClick = onOpenTtsSetup, modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().height(72.dp)) {\n                Text(\"系统语音设置（备用）\")\n            }\n        }\n\n        OutlinedButton(onClick = onBack, modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().height(72.dp)) { Text(\"返回首页\") }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun QuizScreen(\n    bookTitle: String,\n    mode: QuizMode,\n    unitTitle: String,\n    question: QuizQuestion,\n    promptLanguage: PromptLanguage,\n    index: Int,\n    total: Int,\n    correctCount: Int,\n    selectedAnswer: String?,\n    answered: Boolean,\n    hintMessage: String?,\n    practiceAvailable: Boolean,\n    practiceListening: Boolean,\n    practiceStatusMessage: String,\n    practiceResult: SpeechPracticeResult?,\n    practiceRewardMessage: String?,\n    practiceRewardDetails: List<String>,\n    practiceRewardBadges: List<Badge>,\n    repairedWordsMessage: String?,\n    sentenceRetryLabel: String?,\n    onRetrySentencePractice: (() -> Unit)?,\n    onSpeakPrompt: () -> Unit,\n    onPracticePrompt: () -> Unit,\n    onSpeakAnswer: () -> Unit,\n    onPracticeAnswer: () -> Unit,\n    onSpeakWord: (String) -> Unit,\n    onPracticeWord: (String) -> Unit,\n    onAnswer: (String) -> Unit,\n    onNext: () -> Unit,\n    onBack: () -> Unit,\n) {\n    val prompt = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.ZH) question.promptZh else question.promptEn\n    val options = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.ZH) question.optionsEn else question.optionsZh\n    val correctAnswer = if (promptLanguage == PromptLanguage.ZH) question.answerEn else question.answerZh\n    val practiceMissedWords = practiceResult?.score?.targetWordFeedback.orEmpty().filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\n\n[306 more lines in file. Use offset=1260 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773624354593}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e02ad6c","parentId":"557fc982","timestamp":"2026-03-16T01:26:23.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating build.gradle updates**\n\nI’m considering whether I need to update the build.gradle file to include any asset folder, but it’s not strictly necessary if files are added under the assets. I think maybe a docs file could help with bundled layout instructions, but I also wonder if I should create an empty directory marker like `.gitkeep`. If I add a README file in the assets, it should get copied, which might be more useful than just the asset folder itself. I also want to ensure I check the compile/build process afterward and prepare the release APK accordingly.\n\n**Planning APK builds**\n\nI think it’s better to build both APKs and potentially install verification. I might check if there's an emulator I can use from memory, and consider using adb to install. I should ensure I at least build it, since the user wants to see the APK today, so delivering that path might happen either now or later. If the build succeeds, I can work on producing an optimized APK. I should also commit changes and check the file package name, as the paths might differ, but edits should be manageable.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_04b76fdf640436710169b75c25a88881a0a759d275d8e64f7a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpt1w50d70VFaYlFJXE-GgpfOaaYDGUk9o2R_Lyj9fwIhVF-wsX8KvWlNC-q55lv8tSFWhMwEFFydybkh0fXNI3LIy7N6UkBtieJmUDR5fJhQCMm_kuhS8xF5gXGF8fvuC-gq7jLOk1NnqB7aTF4iKEPjAD5zXxfXpjAbcJcUmjcjaKrqUkBRTUiQsGwwY2cM2pJDiBMeVlwh-2MWZWki24YURKaF4UYhXMkPoVhli2r88OQQbeeZF3bW6kv_iv3x-s5o62Fgh4iatJuUeDfRMf1pt9_-FrbBCMUHg_5IVq8es08VuDYTyvhXZFAZsSl0gdN5ShgJOqz0XE_y--HaSIOPnGL_mKW4lPJLvJNxK9e7dzmy0IEEFhjvNIrJg-OSYqRLCqyiEnAMSvIJdzQf_w08zgw2Il-phXDIhtgr6XU05Xi3ks-l9wcsmlBBp91yfCHArgxKspNSpT3dIvqB8-SniD8VmycGXy4yo2Na8zucdjSYd1SH4fplq69ErQmcI_qaqkkZmgZsWdouNQKuqgNfS-gJWsFnY3Tl017YsivXVJYiDWBEgiFJDF1u5VI89l7aiB16H