uld help with bundled layout instructions, but I also wonder if I should create an empty directory marker like `.gitkeep`. If I add a README file in the assets, it should get copied, which might be more useful than just the asset folder itself. I also want to ensure I check the compile/build process afterward and prepare the release APK accordingly.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Planning APK builds**\\n\\nI think it’s better to build both APKs and potentially install verification. I might check if there's an emulator I can use from memory, and consider using adb to install. I should ensure I at least build it, since the user wants to see the APK today, so delivering that path might happen either now or later. If the build succeeds, I can work on producing an optimized APK. I should also commit changes and check the file package name, as the paths might differ, but edits should be manageable.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我现在落两个真实改动：  \n1) **sherpa 未就绪时自动回退系统语音**，避免把跟读入口搞成“选了就不能用”  \n2) **如果以后把模型放进 APK 资源里，首启自动落地到可用目录**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04b76fdf640436710169b75c39fa0481a08b66602d87a1ffac\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_KTBttFI6eCpB0gz2GRbLKZ6D|fc_04b76fdf640436710169b75c3a138c81a0a98784e70b187bae","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeEngineFactory.kt","oldText":"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\n    fun create(\n        context: Context,\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\n        }\n    }\n}\n","newText":"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\n    fun create(\n        context: Context,\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> {\n                val modelManager = com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.SherpaOnnxModelManager(context)\n                val sherpaSettings = settingsRepository.sherpaOnnxSettings()\n                val sherpaReady = sherpaSettings.enabled && modelManager.inspect(sherpaSettings.modelId).isReady\n                if (sherpaReady) {\n                    SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\n                } else {\n                    SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeEngineFactory.kt\",\"oldText\":\"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\\n    fun create(\\n        context: Context,\\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\",\"newText\":\"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\\n    fun create(\\n        context: Context,\\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> {\\n                val modelManager = com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.SherpaOnnxModelManager(context)\\n                val sherpaSettings = settingsRepository.sherpaOnnxSettings()\\n                val sherpaReady = sherpaSettings.enabled && modelManager.inspect(sherpaSettings.modelId).isReady\\n                if (sherpaReady) {\\n                    SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\\n                } else {\\n                    SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35653,"output":1270,"cacheRead":75904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773624354600}}
