lass research and are relevant, exciting and inspiring.  \\n   * [Academic Research, Teaching and Learning](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/universitypress)  \\n   * [English](https://www.cambridgeenglish.org)  \\n   * [International Education](https://www.cambridgeinternational.org/)  \\n   * [Educational resources for schools](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/education)  \\n   * [Bibles](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/universitypress/bibles)  \\n   * [Cambridge OCR](https://ocr.org.uk)  \\n   * [Educational Research](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/educational-research)  \\n   * [The Assessment Network](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/the-assessment-network)  \\n   * [Cambridge Insight](https://www.cambridge.org/insight)  \\n   * [Partnership for Education](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/partnership)  \\n   * [Cambridge Dictionary](https://dictionary.cambridge.org)  \\n   * [The Cambridge Mathematics Project](https://www.cambridgemaths.org)  \\n   * [Bookshop](https://www.cambridgebookshop.co.uk/)  \\nClick to close sub-menu\\n* [About us](#)  \\nCambridge University Press & Assessment  \\n## About us  \\nWe unlock the potential of millions of people worldwide. Our assessments, publications and research spread knowledge, spark enquiry and aid understanding around the world.  \\n   * [About us](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/about-us)  \\n   * [Our story](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/our-story)  \\n   * [Archives and Heritage](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/archives-and-heritage)  \\n   * [People and planet](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/people-and-planet)  \\n   About us [P