internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.\\n\\n#### Strictly Necessary Cookies\\n\\nThese cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.\\n\\n### Cookie List\\n\\nClear\\n\\n*   - [x] checkbox label label \\n\\nApply Cancel\\n\\nConsent Leg.Interest\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\nReject all cookies Save and close\\n\\n[![Image 3: Powered by Onetrust](https://cdn-ukwest.onetrust.com/logos/static/powered_by_logo.svg)](https://www.onetrust.com/products/cookie-consent/)\\n\", \"attempts\": [{\"source\": \"markdown.new\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\": 500, \"resolved_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"preview\": \"{\\\"success\\\":false,\\\"error\\\":\\\"Error from The API: All conversion methods failed. The page might be empty or inaccessible.\\\"}\"}, {\"source\": \"defuddle.md\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://defuddle.md/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\": 200, \"resolved_url\": \"https://defuddle.md/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"preview\": \"---\\nsource: \\\"https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\\\"\\nlanguage: \\\"en\\\"\\n---\"}, {\"source\": \"r.jina.ai\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://r.jina.ai/http://https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\