\\nQty: –  + Delete  \\n**You have reached the maximum limit for this item**\\n\\n\\\\+ 1 more item in your bag\\n\\n**Subtotal** \\n\\nYour bag is empty.\\n\\n Continue shopping [Checkout](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/checkout/#/bag) \\n\\n###### Item added to bagSorry, there was a problem getting your bag informationItem cannot be purchased with the existing contents of your bagItem unavailable online\\n\\n[ ✕](javascript:;) \\n\\n was added to your bag.\\n\\nPlease try again.\\n\\nSorry, this item cannot be purchased in the same transaction as the existing items in your bag.   \\n  \\n Please complete the purchase of the items currently in your bag and then add this item in a separate transaction or visit [Shopping Help](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/shopping-help#education-credit-account-order-mixed-bag-items).\\n\\nSorry, this product is not currently available to buy online. Please visit [Shopping Help](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/shopping-help#unavailable-items-to-buy-online).\\n\\nContinue Shopping [View bag and checkout](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/checkout/#/bag) \\n\\n[ ](javascript:;) \\n\\n###### Remove item\\n\\n[ ✕](javascript:;) \\n\\nAre you sure you want to remove  from your bag?\\n\\nRemove item Keep \\n\\n[ ](javascript:;) \\n\\n---\\n\\n## Breadcrumb\\n\\n1. [Home](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb)\\n\\n# You're lost in Cambridge.\\n\\nThe page you are looking for can't be found. Visit our [homepage](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb), or use the links above.\\n\\nImage: by kind permission of Ivy Leswekjfe FRS and Gonville and Caius College\\n\\n## The Senate House car stunt\\n\\nOn 8 June 1958, Peter Davey and 11 other students at Gonville & Cauis college hoisted a derelict Austin 7 van onto the roof of the Cambridge University Senate House, in the most ingenious of student pranks. Although the students had taken three hours under the cover of darkness to hoist the van onto the roof, it took the Civil Defence force, helped by the Police and Fire Brigade four days to remove it. The then Dean of Gonville & Caius, the Rev. Hugh Montefiore, having an idea of who was responsible for the stunt, sent a case of champagne to the halls of residence at Gonville & Caius where Peter Davey's room was located.\\n\\n[  ](/) \\n\\n##  What we do  What we do \\n\\n* [Academic Research, Teaching and Learning](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/universitypress)\\n* [English](https://www.cambridgeenglish.org)\\n* [International Education](https://www.cambridgeinternational.org/)\\n* [Educational resources for schools](https://www.cambridge.org/education)\\n* [Bibles](https://www.cambridge.org/bibles)\\n* [Partnership for Education](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/partnership)\\n* [Author support](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/authorhub)\\n* [Bookshop](https://www.cambridgebookshop.co.uk/)\\n* [Educational Research](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/educational-research)\\n* [The Assessment Network](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/the-assessment-network)\\n* [Cambridge OCR](https://ocr.org.uk/)\\n\\n##  About us  About us \\n\\n* [About us](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power/gb/about-us)\\n* [Our story](https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog\", \"attempts\": [{\"source\": \"markdown.new\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power\", \"status\": 200, \"resolved_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power\", \"preview\": \"Title: You're lost in Cambridge.\\n\\nURL Source: https://www.cambridge.org/gb/cambridgeenglish/catalog/primary/power\\n\\nMarkdown Content:\\n[ Skip to main content](#main-content) \\n\\n You are viewing content i\"}]}\n\n=== oxford discover ===\n{\"ok\": true, \"requested_url\": \"https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"method\": \"mirror\", \"source\": \"r.jina.ai\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://r.jina.ai/http://https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"resolved_url\": \"https://r.jina.ai/http://https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"content\": \"Title: Page not found | English Language Teaching\\n\\nURL Source: https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\\n\\nWarning: Target URL returned error 404: Not Found\\n\\nMarkdown Content:\\nPage not found | English Language Teaching | Oxford University Press\\n===============\\n\\n[![Image 1: Oxford University Press English Language Teaching home](https://elt.oup.com/error-page/elt/img/oup-logo.svg)](https://elt.oup.com/ \\\"Oxford University Press English Language Teaching home\\\")English Language Teaching\\n\\n[Skip to content](https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/#content)\\n\\nPage not found\\n==============\\n\\nSorry but the page you're looking for cannot be found. The address may have changed or the page is no longer available.\\n\\nSearch\\n------\\n\\nSearch\\n\\nAll\\n\\nGo to...\\n--------\\n\\n*   **[Home page](https://elt.oup.com/)**\\n*   **[Catalogue](https://elt.oup.com/cat/)**\\n*   **[Oxford Teachers' Club](https://elt.oup.com/teachersclub/)**\\n*   **[Sitemap](https://elt.oup.com/sitemap)**\\n\\nCopyright © Oxford University Press, 2026. All Rights Reserved.\\n\\nOxford University Press uses cookies to enhance your experience on our website. By selecting ‘accept all’ you are agreeing to our use of cookies. You can change your cookie settings at any time. More information can be found in our [Cookie Policy](https://corp.oup.com/cookie-policy/). \\n\\nReject and manage cookies Accept all cookies\\n\\n![Image 2: Company Logo](https://cdn-ukwest.onetrust.com/logos/static/ot_company_logo.png)\\n\\nCookie Consent Management\\n-------------------------\\n\\nWhen you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. Allowing us to store cookies on your device allows us to give you a more personalized experience. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer. \\n\\n[Cookie Policy](https://corp.oup.com/cookie-policy/)\\n\\nAccept all cookies\\n\\n#### Functional Cookies\\n\\n- [x] Functional Cookies \\n\\nThese cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.\\n\\n#### Performance Cookies\\n\\n- [x] Performance Cookies \\n\\nThese cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.\\n\\n#### Targeting Cookies\\n\\n- [x] Targeting Cookies \\n\\nThese cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.\\n\\n#### Strictly Necessary Cookies\\n\\nThese cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.\\n\\n### Cookie List\\n\\nClear\\n\\n*   - [x] checkbox label label \\n\\nApply Cancel\\n\\nConsent Leg.Interest\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\n- [x] checkbox label label\\n\\nReject all cookies Save and close\\n\\n[![Image 3: Powered by Onetrust](https://cdn-ukwest.onetrust.com/logos/static/powered_by_logo.svg)](https://www.onetrust.com/products/cookie-consent/)\\n\", \"attempts\": [{\"source\": \"markdown.new\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\": 500, \"resolved_url\": \"https://markdown.new/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"preview\": \"{\\\"success\\\":false,\\\"error\\\":\\\"Error from The API: All conversion methods failed. The page might be empty or inaccessible.\\\"}\"}, {\"source\": \"defuddle.md\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://defuddle.md/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\": 200, \"resolved_url\": \"https://defuddle.md/https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"preview\": \"---\\nsource: \\\"https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\\\"\\nlanguage: \\\"en\\\"\\n---\"}, {\"source\": \"r.jina.ai\", \"mirror_url\": \"https://r.jina.ai/http://https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"status\": 200, \"resolved_url\": \"https://r.jina.ai/http://https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\", \"preview\": \"Title: Page not found | English Language Teaching\\n\\nURL Source: https://elt.oup.com/catalogue/items/global/skills/oxford_discover/\\n\\nWarning: Target URL returned error 404: Not Found\\n\\nMarkdown Content:\\n\"}]}\n","name":"set python3"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773626829441}}
