{"type":"message","id":"16d21639","parentId":"e45b7f08","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:31:39.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still having issues. TLS errors and 404s. Let me give a more honest status update to the user. I've been trying but hitting a lot of dead ends. It's time to be transparent and ask for either:1. Specific links they can provide2. Alternative approach3. Permission to use a different source\n\nLet me write a concise update.","thinkingSignature":"53d4cf5f91fdcee47f968d9a8d62c23e5cbb90a1ba5aec16dbcd48579d5a0594"},{"type":"text","text":"**我这轮的结果：**\n\n- 官方教材站：OUP、Cambridge 入口已改，404\n- 第三方站：EnglishClub、FluentU、KizPhonics 也404或被墙\n- 抓取链路：TLS 握手失败、curl 超时\n\n**我试过的方向：**\n- Family and Friends\n- Power Up\n- Oxford Discover\n- Phonics scope and sequence\n- ESL vocabulary lists\n\n命中率很低。\n\n---\n\n**现在有两个选择：**\n\n1. **你能不能给我 1~2 个你知道有效的资料链接？**  \n   你手上如果有已买的教材配套 PDF、或者你之前下过的教学大纲页，发给我一个具体 URL，我就能直接抓。\n\n2. **如果暂时没有具体链接，我换个方向**  \n   - 先不做这几套教材的公开资料调研\n   - 回到 app 本身的交付，先把现有 Level 1~6 的内容体系和交互体验打磨好\n   - 教材对齐工作往后排\n\n你说一句，我按你说的继续。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":96923,"output":286,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773628275756}}
