s\n3. Multiple parallel searches\n\nI should acknowledge this and maybe try to use firecrawl myself in the future, or note that this is a tool I should have access to.","thinkingSignature":"001af1f9723fe0ef66a75e2dbfb76a3dccbe91958cf12bb28ae39d31e9d5de6f"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，我已经读到了。\n\n**trae 的方法我记住了：**\n\n1. 用 `firecrawl search` + 精准关键词\n2. 多线并行搜索\n3. 最后模型汇总\n\n这套链路比我之前试的：\n- 直接抓官网 URL（404）\n- 镜像链路的 TLS 握手失败\n-  browser snapshot 超时\n\n**要靠谱得多。**\n\n---\n\n**这份资料我上一条已经落地了：**\n\n- 文档路径：`apps/kids-box-tv-app/docs/app-content-plan-reference.md`\n\n内容包括：\n- Phonics 5 阶段体系\n- Power Up / Family and Friends / Oxford Discover 级别划分\n- 内容结构特色\n- CEFR 对照表\n- App 内容优先级\n\n---\n\n**我后面遇到类似调研需求，会优先用 `firecrawl search` + 精准关键词这个方法。**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":44,"output":611,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":129165,"totalTokens":129820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773628359816}}
