{"type":"message","id":"d1d5eafd","parentId":"f87c4382","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:08.460Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the error message display logic around line 959, which shows \"提示：$errorMessage\". The error is coming from `speechPracticeRecognizer.statusMessage`. I need to see what's happening in the SpeechPracticeRecognizer and what error code is being returned.\n\nLet me also check the SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine to see what happens when it's used.","thinkingSignature":"f36f6ae955aa7c5575e13fbc1ffb08669ef62b6ae2693a530fe74ffe436b8a7c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rzs839phivaw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","limit":100,"offset":170}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":100633,"output":156,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629400222}}
{"type":"message","id":"0148339b","parentId":"d1d5eafd","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:08.513Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rzs839phivaw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n                override fun onBeginningOfSpeech() {\n                    isListening = true\n                    statusMessage = \"正在听…\"\n                }\n\n                override fun onRmsChanged(rmsdB: Float) = Unit\n\n                override fun onBufferReceived(buffer: ByteArray?) = Unit\n\n                override fun onEndOfSpeech() {\n                    isListening = false\n                    statusMessage = \"识别中…\"\n                }\n\n                override fun onError(error: Int) {\n                    isListening = false\n                    lastErrorCode = error\n                    lastErrorAttemptId = currentAttemptId\n                    statusMessage = mapError(error)\n                }\n\n                override fun onResults(results: Bundle?) {\n                    isListening = false\n                    val matches = results?.getStringArrayList(SpeechRecognizer.RESULTS_RECOGNITION).orEmpty()\n                    applyRecognitionMatches(matches)\n                }\n\n                override fun onPartialResults(partialResults: Bundle?) = Unit\n\n                override fun onEvent(eventType: Int, params: Bundle?) = Unit\n            })\n        }\n    }\n\n    override fun handleFallbackResult(data: Intent?): Boolean {\n        isListening = false\n        val matches = data?.getStringArrayListExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_RESULTS).orEmpty()\n        return applyRecognitionMatches(matches)\n    }\n\n    override fun handleFallbackCancelled() {\n        isListening = false\n        statusMessage = \"已取消跟读\"\n    }\n\n    private fun applyRecognitionMatches(matches: List<String>): Boolean {\n        val recognized = matches.firstOrNull().orEmpty().trim()\n        if (recognized.isBlank()) {\n            statusMessage = \"没听清，再试一次\"\n            lastResult = null\n            return false\n        }\n        val score = ReadAlongScorer.score(currentTargetText, recognized)\n        lastResult = SpeechPracticeResult(\n            attemptId = currentAttemptId,\n            targetLabel = currentTargetLabel,\n            targetRewardId = currentTargetRewardId,\n            score = score,\n        )\n        statusMessage = \"${score.encouragementTitle}，${score.encouragementDetail}\"\n        return true\n    }\n\n    private fun buildIntent(\n        action: String = RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH,\n        forceEnglish: Boolean,\n        includePrompt: Boolean,\n    ): Intent {\n        return Intent(action).apply {\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_MODEL, RecognizerIntent.LANGUAGE_MODEL_FREE_FORM)\n            if (forceEnglish) {\n                putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n                putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_PREFERENCE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            }\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_MAX_RESULTS, 3)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PARTIAL_RESULTS, false)\n            if (includePrompt) {\n                putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PROMPT, \"请跟读英文\")\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun initialStatus(): String {\n        return if (isAvailable()) {\n            \"点击按钮开始跟读打分\"\n        } else {\n            \"未检测到系统语音识别服务\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun mapError(error: Int): String {\n        return when (error) {\n            SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_AUDIO -> \"录音失败，请检查麦克风（code=$error, ${debugSummary()}）\"\n            SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_CLIENT -> \"语音识别被中断，请再试一次（code=$error, ${debugSummary()}）\"\n            SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS -> {\n                if (hasMicPermission()) {\n                    \"系统语音识别服务未能正常访问麦克风，请检查系统语音输入服务或重启后再试（code=$error, ${debugSummary()}）\"\n                } else {\n                    \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问（code=$error, ${debugSummary()}）\"\n\n[12 more lines in file. Use offset=270 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773629408507}}
{"type":"message","id":"5b76e396","parentId":"0148339b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:16.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue. The error could be coming from several places:\n1. `SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_AUDIO` - \"录音失败\"\n2. `SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_CLIENT` - \"语音识别被中断\"\n3. `SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS` - Permission issues\n4. Other error codes\n\nThe issue could also be related to Sherpa - let me check SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine to see what's happening there.","thinkingSignature":"097ed55f377b6cfc555ff9b82154f970b35e140e2c482d1f2f5c42d9aee02367"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5ohf8kl8ik6v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine.kt","limit":100,"offset":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":101631,"output":179,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629408515}}
{"type":"message","id":"e0e02f73","parentId":"5b76e396","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:16.644Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5ohf8kl8ik6v_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            val recognized = currentRuntime.recognize(merged)\n            if (recognized.isBlank()) {\n                postNoMatch(attemptId)\n                return\n            }\n\n            val score = ReadAlongScorer.score(currentTargetText, recognized)\n            postToMain {\n                if (attemptId != currentAttemptId) return@postToMain\n                lastResult = SpeechPracticeResult(\n                    attemptId = attemptId,\n                    targetLabel = currentTargetLabel,\n                    targetRewardId = currentTargetRewardId,\n                    score = score,\n                )\n                statusMessage = \"${score.encouragementTitle}，${score.encouragementDetail}\"\n            }\n        } catch (t: Throwable) {\n            postToMain {\n                if (attemptId != currentAttemptId) return@postToMain\n                isListening = false\n                lastErrorCode = 1\n                lastErrorAttemptId = attemptId\n                statusMessage = \"离线识别暂时不可用：${t.message ?: \"请稍后再试\"}\"\n            }\n        } finally {\n            runCatching { pcmRecorder.stop() }\n            runCatching { pcmRecorder.release() }\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun stopRecognition(resetStatus: Boolean) {\n        stopRequested = true\n        runCatching { pcmRecorder.stop() }\n        runCatching { pcmRecorder.release() }\n        workerThread = null\n        if (resetStatus) {\n            isListening = false\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun mergeChunks(chunks: List<ShortArray>, totalSamples: Int): ShortArray {\n        if (chunks.isEmpty() || totalSamples <= 0) return shortArrayOf()\n        val merged = ShortArray(totalSamples)\n        var offset = 0\n        chunks.forEach { chunk ->\n            chunk.copyInto(merged, destinationOffset = offset)\n            offset += chunk.size\n        }\n        return merged\n    }\n\n    private fun postNoMatch(attemptId: Int) {\n        postToMain {\n            if (attemptId != currentAttemptId) return@postToMain\n            isListening = false\n            lastResult = null\n            statusMessage = \"没听清，再试一次\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun postToMain(block: () -> Unit) {\n        mainHandler.post(block)\n    }\n\n    private fun initialStatus(): String {\n        val mode = settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()\n        val settings = settingsRepository.sherpaOnnxSettings()\n        val status = modelManager.inspect(settings.modelId)\n        return when {\n            mode.name != \"SHERPA_ONNX\" -> \"当前未启用 sherpa-onnx\"\n            !settings.enabled -> \"sherpa-onnx 尚未启用，请先完成模型接入\"\n            !status.isReady -> \"sherpa-onnx 模型未就绪：${status.modelDirPath}\"\n            else -> \"点击按钮开始离线跟读\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773629416635}}
{"type":"message","id":"343ed134","parentId":"e0e02f73","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:25.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. Looking at the code:\n\n1. If Sherpa is enabled but the model is not ready, it will show \"sherpa-onnx 模型未就绪\"\n2. If Sherpa throws an exception, it will show \"离线识别暂时不可用：${t.message}\"\n\nBut the user said they're getting \"提示：似乎出错了呢\" - which is a generic error message. This might be coming from somewhere else.\n\nWait, I added the fallback logic earlier - let me check what happens when Sherpa fails and it falls back to the system recognizer. Let me also check the error handling in the factory.\n\nActually, the issue might be related to Sherpa being selected but the model not being ready, which would cause the Sherpa engine to fail. Or there might be an issue with the audio recording itself.\n\nLet me look at the PcmAudioRecorder to see if there could be an issue there.","thinkingSignature":"c4ebbcc2e77be5359d9c782b620cd9e4665b01af3f5e0c478cfdf91255a74a1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aq7hjdxljn7l_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/PcmAudioRecorder.kt","limit":80,"offset":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":102431,"output":271,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629416650}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6417dee","parentId":"343ed134","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:25.137Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_aq7hjdxljn7l_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.media.AudioFormat\nimport android.media.AudioRecord\nimport android.media.MediaRecorder\nimport kotlin.math.max\n\nclass PcmAudioRecorder(\n    private val config: Config = Config(),\n) {\n    data class Config(\n        val sampleRate: Int = 16000,\n        val channelConfig: Int = AudioFormat.CHANNEL_IN_MONO,\n        val audioFormat: Int = AudioFormat.ENCODING_PCM_16BIT,\n        val readMultiplier: Int = 2,\n    )\n\n    private var audioRecord: AudioRecord? = null\n    private var bufferSizeInBytes: Int = 0\n\n    fun prepare(): Boolean {\n        release()\n        val minBuffer = AudioRecord.getMinBufferSize(config.sampleRate, config.channelConfig, config.audioFormat)\n        if (minBuffer <= 0) return false\n        bufferSizeInBytes = max(minBuffer, minBuffer * config.readMultiplier)\n        audioRecord = AudioRecord(\n            MediaRecorder.AudioSource.MIC,\n            config.sampleRate,\n            config.channelConfig,\n            config.audioFormat,\n            bufferSizeInBytes,\n        )\n        return audioRecord?.state == AudioRecord.STATE_INITIALIZED\n    }\n\n    fun start(): Boolean {\n        val recorder = audioRecord ?: return false\n        if (recorder.state != AudioRecord.STATE_INITIALIZED) return false\n        recorder.startRecording()\n        return recorder.recordingState == AudioRecord.RECORDSTATE_RECORDING\n    }\n\n    fun readChunk(): ShortArray {\n        val recorder = audioRecord ?: return shortArrayOf()\n        if (bufferSizeInBytes <= 0) return shortArrayOf()\n        val shortBuffer = ShortArray(bufferSizeInBytes / 2)\n        val read = recorder.read(shortBuffer, 0, shortBuffer.size)\n        return if (read > 0) shortBuffer.copyOf(read) else shortArrayOf()\n    }\n\n    fun stop() {\n        runCatching { audioRecord?.stop() }\n    }\n\n    fun release() {\n        runCatching { audioRecord?.release() }\n        audioRecord = null\n        bufferSizeInBytes = 0\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773629425126}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8c55503","parentId":"f6417dee","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:33.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see a potential issue. The PcmAudioRecorder requires the MIC permission and the AudioRecord needs to be properly initialized. If the prepare() or start() methods return false, the Sherpa engine might fail silently.\n\nAlso, looking at the error message, it seems like there could be a few issues:\n1. The Sherpa model might not be ready (we added the fallback, but the user is still getting an error)\n2. There might be a crash in the Sherpa runtime itself\n3. The audio recording might be failing\n\nLet me check what happens when Sherpa fails - does it properly fall back to the system recognizer? Let me look at the fallback logic in the UI again.","thinkingSignature":"ab9fb12a1e33c5d09145a2b59ff7b3bf0ff032a2bb5a9cf1218a4e7881bf3c80"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xae5exw1ksgn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt","limit":60,"offset":250}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":103169,"output":223,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629425140}}
{"type":"message","id":"445ff8b6","parentId":"b8c55503","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:33.448Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xae5exw1ksgn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        sentenceRetryInProgress = false\n    }\n\n    LaunchedEffect(speechPracticeRecognizer.lastErrorAttemptId, speechPracticeRecognizer.lastErrorCode) {\n        val errorAttemptId = speechPracticeRecognizer.lastErrorAttemptId\n        val errorCode = speechPracticeRecognizer.lastErrorCode\n        if (errorAttemptId == 0 || errorAttemptId == lastAutoFallbackAttemptId) return@LaunchedEffect\n        if (!speechPracticeRecognizer.shouldAutoFallback(errorCode)) return@LaunchedEffect\n        val fallbackIntent = speechPracticeRecognizer.buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget()\n        if (fallbackIntent != null) {\n            lastAutoFallbackAttemptId = errorAttemptId\n            fallbackSpeechLauncher.launch(fallbackIntent)\n            errorMessage = null\n        }\n    }\n\n    LaunchedEffect(speechPracticeRecognizer.lastResult?.attemptId, currentBookId) {\n        val result = speechPracticeRecognizer.lastResult ?: return@LaunchedEffect\n        if (result.attemptId == 0 || result.attemptId == lastProcessedPracticeAttemptId) return@LaunchedEffect\n        lastProcessedPracticeAttemptId = result.attemptId\n        val reward = progressRepository.awardPracticeReward(\n            bookId = currentBookId,\n            rewardId = result.targetRewardId,\n            practiceScore = result.score.score,\n        )\n        if (reward.gainedStars > 0) {\n            practiceBonusStars += reward.gainedStars\n            practiceRewardMessage = \"跟读奖励 +${reward.gainedStars} 星，已计入总星星（当前 ⭐ ${reward.totalStars}）\"\n            practiceRewardDetails = reward.rewardBreakdown\n            practiceRewardBadges = (practiceRewardBadges + reward.newBadges).distinctBy { it.id }\n            rewardCelebrationMessage = practiceRewardMessage\n            rewardCelebrationStars = reward.gainedStars\n            rewardCelebrationBadges = reward.newBadges\n            showRewardCelebrationDialog = true\n            lastTotalStars = reward.totalStars\n        } else {\n            practiceRewardDetails = reward.rewardBreakdown\n            practiceRewardMessage = if (reward.alreadyRewarded) {\n                \"这个跟读奖励已经领过了\"\n            } else {\n                null\n            }\n        }\n\n        if (result.targetLabel == \"逐词跟读\" && result.score.score >= 80) {\n            val retryText = activeSentencePracticeText\n            val retryLabel = activeSentencePracticeLabel\n            val retryRewardId = activeSentencePracticeRewardId\n            if (!retryText.isNullOrBlank() && !retryLabel.isNullOrBlank() && !retryRewardId.isNullOrBlank()) {\n                sentenceRetryText = retryText\n                sentenceRetryLabel = retryLabel\n                sentenceRetryRewardId = retryRewardId\n                speechSpeaker.speak(retryText)\n            }\n        }\n\n        if (sentenceRetryInProgress && result.targetLabel != \"逐词跟读\") {\n            repairedWordsMessage = if (result.score.score >= 80 && repairedWordsSnapshot.isNotEmpty()) {\n                \"已修复红词：${repairedWordsSnapshot.joinToString(\"、\")}\"\n            } else if (repairedWordsSnapshot.isNotEmpty()) {\n\n[1277 more lines in file. Use offset=310 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773629433438}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c661e17","parentId":"445ff8b6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:50:40.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. Looking at the fallback logic in the UI:- There's a `shouldAutoFallback` method being called to determine if it should fall back\n- There's a `buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget` method being called\n\nBut wait - the issue is that even if Sherpa fails and falls back to the system recognizer, the error message might still be shown because of the way the UI handles errors.\n\nLet me check what the `shouldAutoFallback` method does and see if it's properly handling Sherpa failures.","thinkingSignature":"5918a1228e1384397656dfc4bddb869156724f71c131dedf772a8ad578ea4268"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z1e2aylvxx4w_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\ngrep -n \"shouldAutoFallback\\|buildFallbackIntent\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":104087,"output":225,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128648,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629433450}}
