{"type":"message","id":"8a62436d","parentId":"de9291fa","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:51:31.540Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full flow. The UI does try to fall back to system speech when Sherpa fails, but only if `buildFallbackIntent` returns a non-null value. Let me check what `buildFallbackIntent` does for Sherpa.","thinkingSignature":"dbdc030c386c5871da97c088572323daef5cb4be33eb88a5a01d7c49dcad19b6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ez2fypocmc2x_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","limit":40,"offset":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":107503,"output":130,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629485110}}
{"type":"message","id":"caede670","parentId":"8a62436d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:51:31.577Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ez2fypocmc2x_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        recognizer?.cancel()\n        recognizer?.startListening(buildIntent(forceEnglish = true, includePrompt = true))\n        return true\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? {\n        if (!preparePracticeTarget(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)) {\n            return null\n        }\n        return buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget()\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? {\n        if (!hasMicPermission()) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            return null\n        }\n        if (currentTargetText.isBlank()) {\n            statusMessage = \"当前题目没有可跟读的英文内容\"\n            return null\n        }\n        val intent = buildIntent(\n            action = RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH,\n            forceEnglish = false,\n            includePrompt = false,\n        )\n        return if (intent.resolveActivity(context.packageManager) != null) {\n            statusMessage = \"正在打开系统语音识别（兼容模式）…\"\n            intent\n        } else {\n            statusMessage = \"系统里没有可用的语音识别界面（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            null\n        }\n    }\n\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean {\n        return error == SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS ||\n            error == SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_CLIENT ||\n            error == SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_SERVER\n    }\n\n[142 more lines in file. Use offset=140 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773629491569}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e082693","parentId":"caede670","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:51:40.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. The `SpeechPracticeRecognizer` (system engine) has a `buildFallbackIntent` method that tries to build a system speech recognition intent. But when Sherpa fails, we need to make sure the fallback intent is created.Actually, wait - when Sherpa fails, the UI code calls `speechPracticeRecognizer.buildFallbackIntent()` - but this is the *current* recognizer, which is Sherpa if Sherpa is selected. Sherpa doesn't have a `buildFallbackIntent` method - it inherits from `SpeechPracticeEngine` which probably returns null.Let me check what `SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine` returns for `buildFallbackIntent`.","thinkingSignature":"31ded46cd5c07b376be6b0e84dd67e92160b69c42780bb2148a1a547ee065bcf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_21p3ygn67gue_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\ngrep -n \"buildFallbackIntent\\|SpeechPracticeEngine\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeEngine.kt","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":107985,"output":255,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132576,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629491580}}
