{"type":"message","id":"e5f96e52","parentId":"8f0a6a01","timestamp":"2026-03-16T02:52:04.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! Sherpa returns `null` for `buildFallbackIntent`, which means when Sherpa fails, the fallback doesn't work properly!\n\nThe fix is:\n1. Make Sherpa's `buildFallbackIntent` actually build a system speech intent (like the system recognizer does)\n2. Or, better yet - make Sherpa properly implement fallback\n\nLet me fix this by making Sherpa return a proper fallback intent.","thinkingSignature":"ecda0c7db6ca14b03bdd1f355761407231ecd535ad1d4b1abcfca86f4eab2676"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根本原因了！**Sherpa 的 `buildFallbackIntent` 返回 `null`**，所以当 Sherpa 失败时，系统无法回退到系统语音。\n\n我来修复这个问题：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_851kjch6vzy7_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine.kt","newText":"    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? {\n        // 当 Sherpa 失败时，构建系统语音识别 intent 作为回退\n        if (targetText.isBlank()) return null\n        val hasPermission = ContextCompat.checkSelfPermission(appContext, Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO) == PackageManager.PERMISSION_GRANTED\n        if (!hasPermission) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问\"\n            return null\n        }\n        val intent = Intent(RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH).apply {\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_MODEL, RecognizerIntent.LANGUAGE_MODEL_FREE_FORM)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_PREFERENCE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_MAX_RESULTS, 3)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PARTIAL_RESULTS, false)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PROMPT, \"请跟读英文\")\n        }\n        return if (intent.resolveActivity(appContext.packageManager) != null) {\n            statusMessage = \"Sherpa 不可用，正在切换到系统语音识别…\"\n            intent\n        } else {\n            statusMessage = \"系统语音识别不可用\"\n            null\n        }\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? {\n        return buildFallbackIntent(currentTargetText, currentTargetLabel, currentTargetRewardId)\n    }","oldText":"    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? = null\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? = null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108517,"output":588,"cacheRead":24336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773629507311}}
