{"type":"message","id":"ada159b0","parentId":"ab2ea25e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:32.137Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到很多地方设置 errorMessage。问题可能是在引擎创建时就失败了。让我看看工厂方法创建引擎的逻辑，以及 startPractice 的错误处理。\n\n关键问题是：SpeechPracticeEngineFactory.create() 可能会在某些情况下返回不可用的引擎。\n\n让我检查工厂方法和 startPractice 的调用流程。实际上，问题可能是：1. 工厂方法创建了 SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine（因为设置里启用了 sherpa）2. 但模型未就绪，所以 startPractice 返回 false\n3. 然后代码尝试 buildFallbackIntent，但 Sherpa 的 buildFallbackIntent 返回 null（在我修复之前）4. 所以 errorMessage 被设置为 statusMessage\n\n等等，我刚才已经修复了 SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine 的 buildFallbackIntent 方法。让我确认修复已经包含在最新 APK 中。\n\n让我检查当前代码状态。","thinkingSignature":"942416706703838a7dc21846d913c4d02f4ecbe437a1deaed240be1a408d6794"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yln6q1vfl60x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\ngrep -A 20 \"buildFallbackIntent\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine.kt | head -30","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":81559,"output":289,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104174,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631283455}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd53939a","parentId":"ada159b0","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:32.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yln6q1vfl60x_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? {\n        // 当 Sherpa 失败时，构建系统语音识别 intent 作为回退\n        if (targetText.isBlank()) return null\n        val hasPermission = ContextCompat.checkSelfPermission(appContext, Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO) == PackageManager.PERMISSION_GRANTED\n        if (!hasPermission) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问\"\n            return null\n        }\n        val intent = Intent(RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH).apply {\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_MODEL, RecognizerIntent.LANGUAGE_MODEL_FREE_FORM)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_PREFERENCE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_MAX_RESULTS, 3)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PARTIAL_RESULTS, false)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PROMPT, \"请跟读英文\")\n        }\n        return if (intent.resolveActivity(appContext.packageManager) != null) {\n            statusMessage = \"Sherpa 不可用，正在切换到系统语音识别…\"\n            intent\n        } else {\n            statusMessage = \"系统语音识别不可用\"\n--\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? {\n        return buildFallbackIntent(currentTargetText, currentTargetLabel, currentTargetRewardId)\n    }\n\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean = false\n\n    override fun handleFallbackResult(data: Intent?): Boolean = false"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":10,"aggregated":"override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? {\n        // 当 Sherpa 失败时，构建系统语音识别 intent 作为回退\n        if (targetText.isBlank()) return null\n        val hasPermission = ContextCompat.checkSelfPermission(appContext, Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO) == PackageManager.PERMISSION_GRANTED\n        if (!hasPermission) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问\"\n            return null\n        }\n        val intent = Intent(RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH).apply {\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_MODEL, RecognizerIntent.LANGUAGE_MODEL_FREE_FORM)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_LANGUAGE_PREFERENCE, Locale.US.toLanguageTag())\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_MAX_RESULTS, 3)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PARTIAL_RESULTS, false)\n            putExtra(RecognizerIntent.EXTRA_PROMPT, \"请跟读英文\")\n        }\n        return if (intent.resolveActivity(appContext.packageManager) != null) {\n            statusMessage = \"Sherpa 不可用，正在切换到系统语音识别…\"\n            intent\n        } else {\n            statusMessage = \"系统语音识别不可用\"\n--\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? {\n        return buildFallbackIntent(currentTargetText, currentTargetLabel, currentTargetRewardId)\n    }\n\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean = false\n\n    override fun handleFallbackResult(data: Intent?): Boolean = false","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631292186}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9fae993","parentId":"cd53939a","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:39.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"修复已经在了。但问题可能是：即使 buildFallbackIntent 返回了 Intent，系统语音弹窗也可能启动失败。让我看看 onPracticeClick 处理 fallback 的逻辑。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. startPractice 返回 false（因为 Sherpa 不可用）\n2. buildFallbackIntent 返回了一个 Intent\n3. fallbackSpeechLauncher.launch(fallbackIntent) 被调用\n4. 但系统语音弹窗启动失败（可能是小米系统的定制问题）5. 然后 fallback 被取消，errorMessage 被显示\n\n让我检查是否有处理 fallback 结果的逻辑。实际上，我需要确保：\n1. 如果 Sherpa 不可用，应该直接使用系统语音，而不是先尝试 Sherpa 再回退\n2. 或者确保回退机制能正常工作\n\n让我重新思考这个问题。最简单的解决方案是：\n- 如果 Sherpa 模式启用但模型未就绪，直接禁用 Sherpa 并使用系统语音\n- 不需要回退逻辑\n\n让我检查工厂方法是否正确处理了这种情况。我之前的修复是在工厂方法里：如果 Sherpa 未就绪，返回系统语音引擎。但可能还有其他地方有问题。让我看看工厂方法的代码。","thinkingSignature":"cfc15415e9011476b2700f50ee2f393274d51d0943dcbb5a2acdfdd61542f7e6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gtvhge3enafk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeEngineFactory.kt"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":82226,"output":279,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104831,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631292199}}
{"type":"message","id":"78facc5d","parentId":"b9fae993","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:39.577Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gtvhge3enafk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.AppSettingsRepository\nimport com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.AsrEngineMode\n\nobject SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\n    fun create(\n        context: Context,\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> {\n                val modelManager = com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.SherpaOnnxModelManager(context)\n                val sherpaSettings = settingsRepository.sherpaOnnxSettings()\n                val sherpaReady = sherpaSettings.enabled && modelManager.inspect(sherpaSettings.modelId).isReady\n                if (sherpaReady) {\n                    SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\n                } else {\n                    SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631299568}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb53b7f6","parentId":"78facc5d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:45.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"工厂方法逻辑看起来是对的：如果 Sherpa 未就绪，返回系统语音引擎。\n\n让我重新思考问题。用户说\"点击跟读题目 -> 给予麦克风权限 -> 弹出提示：似乎出错了\"。\n\n可能的问题：\n1. 权限授予后的处理逻辑有问题2. startPractice 失败后，回退intent 启动失败3. 其他崩溃\n\n让我检查权限授予后的处理逻辑。看 KidsBoxTvApp.kt 的 onPracticeClick 或类似函数。","thinkingSignature":"afc9120fd3d8089efc1932369064fbce52888550ed1bffdbfadf830359ed82e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4jwb7np4yhzr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt","limit":50,"offset":185}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":82733,"output":174,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105233,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631299580}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfd2ba72","parentId":"eb53b7f6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:45.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4jwb7np4yhzr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    }\n    val requestMicPermission = rememberLauncherForActivityResult(ActivityResultContracts.RequestPermission()) { granted ->\n        val targetText = pendingPracticeTargetText\n        val targetLabel = pendingPracticeTargetLabel\n        val targetRewardId = pendingPracticeRewardId\n        pendingPracticeTargetText = null\n        pendingPracticeTargetLabel = null\n        pendingPracticeRewardId = null\n        if (granted && targetText != null && targetLabel != null && targetRewardId != null) {\n            if (!speechPracticeRecognizer.startPractice(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)) {\n                val fallbackIntent = speechPracticeRecognizer.buildFallbackIntent(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)\n                if (fallbackIntent != null) {\n                    fallbackSpeechLauncher.launch(fallbackIntent)\n                    errorMessage = null\n                } else {\n                    errorMessage = speechPracticeRecognizer.statusMessage\n                }\n            } else {\n                errorMessage = null\n            }\n        } else if (!granted) {\n            errorMessage = \"需要麦克风权限才能开始跟读打分\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun startReadAlong(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String) {\n        val granted = ContextCompat.checkSelfPermission(context, Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO) == PackageManager.PERMISSION_GRANTED\n        if (granted) {\n            if (!speechPracticeRecognizer.startPractice(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)) {\n                val fallbackIntent = speechPracticeRecognizer.buildFallbackIntent(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)\n                if (fallbackIntent != null) {\n                    fallbackSpeechLauncher.launch(fallbackIntent)\n                    errorMessage = null\n                } else {\n                    errorMessage = speechPracticeRecognizer.statusMessage\n                }\n            } else {\n                errorMessage = null\n            }\n        } else {\n            pendingPracticeTargetText = targetText\n            pendingPracticeTargetLabel = targetLabel\n            pendingPracticeRewardId = targetRewardId\n            requestMicPermission.launch(Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO)\n        }\n    }\n\n    LaunchedEffect(currentIndex, questions) {\n        speechPracticeRecognizer.reset()\n        lastAutoFallbackAttemptId = 0\n\n[1352 more lines in file. Use offset=235 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631305469}}
{"type":"message","id":"cfaa0ba8","parentId":"dfd2ba72","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:51.636Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了！逻辑是：1. 权限授予后\n2. 调用 startPractice\n3. 如果 startPractice 返回 false\n4. 调用 buildFallbackIntent\n5. 如果返回非null，启动 fallback intent\n6. 否则显示 errorMessage\n\n问题可能是：\n- 工厂方法已经返回了系统语音引擎（如果 Sherpa 未就绪）- 但代码仍然尝试 buildFallbackIntent\n\n让我检查 startPractice 在系统语音引擎下是否可能返回 false。如果系统语音不可用，startPractice 会返回 false，然后 buildFallbackIntent 会返回 null（因为系统语音本身不可用），所以 errorMessage 被设置。\n\n让我看看 SpeechPracticeRecognizer.startPractice 的逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"0387918126f50e0e7b73c97cfa7e7488ea2d0247105bd1d367a1dba83e880df3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yemaeuvvbvql_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","limit":40,"offset":70}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":83396,"output":217,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105939,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631305482}}
{"type":"message","id":"3564ba24","parentId":"cfaa0ba8","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:51.684Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yemaeuvvbvql_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    private fun preparePracticeTarget(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Boolean {\n        if (!hasMicPermission()) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            return false\n        }\n        val normalizedTarget = targetText.trim()\n        if (normalizedTarget.isBlank()) {\n            statusMessage = \"当前题目没有可跟读的英文内容\"\n            return false\n        }\n        currentTargetText = normalizedTarget\n        currentTargetLabel = targetLabel\n        currentTargetRewardId = targetRewardId.trim()\n        currentAttemptId = nextAttemptId++\n        lastResult = null\n        lastErrorCode = 0\n        lastErrorAttemptId = 0\n        return true\n    }\n\n    override fun startPractice(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Boolean {\n        if (!preparePracticeTarget(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)) {\n            return false\n        }\n        if (!isAvailable()) {\n            statusMessage = \"未检测到系统语音识别服务，请检查系统语音输入/Google 语音识别是否可用（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            return false\n        }\n        ensureRecognizer()\n        statusMessage = \"准备开始，请对着麦克风读出来\"\n        recognizer?.cancel()\n        recognizer?.startListening(buildIntent(forceEnglish = true, includePrompt = true))\n        return true\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Intent? {\n        if (!preparePracticeTarget(targetText, targetLabel, targetRewardId)) {\n            return null\n        }\n        return buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget()\n\n[172 more lines in file. Use offset=110 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631311674}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd498b15","parentId":"3564ba24","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:57.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！\n\n`SpeechPracticeRecognizer.startPractice` 调用了 `isAvailable()` 来检查系统语音是否可用。如果不可用，返回 false 并设置 statusMessage。\n\n然后代码调用 `buildFallbackIntent`，它调用 `preparePracticeTarget`，但这个方法在 `SpeechPracticeRecognizer` 里会检查 `hasMicPermission()`。如果权限已经授予（因为用户已经授权），这个检查应该通过。\n\n但是！`buildFallbackIntent` 最终会调用 `buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget`，它尝试构建一个系统语音 Intent。但如果 `intent.resolveActivity()` 返回 null（小米设备上没有可用的语音识别 Activity），它会返回 null。\n\n这就是问题所在！\n\n让我看看 buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget 在 SpeechPracticeRecognizer 里的实现。","thinkingSignature":"841fa522f3249cde243bb03ebb9899d421f269e514422f36cbd6db12c3abc3a7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iziglgktq07z_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","limit":30,"offset":108}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":84007,"output":231,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106564,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631311687}}
{"type":"message","id":"7493764c","parentId":"fd498b15","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:57.677Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_iziglgktq07z_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        }\n        return buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget()\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): Intent? {\n        if (!hasMicPermission()) {\n            statusMessage = \"App 还没有麦克风权限，请在系统设置里允许麦克风访问（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            return null\n        }\n        if (currentTargetText.isBlank()) {\n            statusMessage = \"当前题目没有可跟读的英文内容\"\n            return null\n        }\n        val intent = buildIntent(\n            action = RecognizerIntent.ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH,\n            forceEnglish = false,\n            includePrompt = false,\n        )\n        return if (intent.resolveActivity(context.packageManager) != null) {\n            statusMessage = \"正在打开系统语音识别（兼容模式）…\"\n            intent\n        } else {\n            statusMessage = \"系统里没有可用的语音识别界面（${debugSummary()}）\"\n            null\n        }\n    }\n\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean {\n        return error == SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_INSUFFICIENT_PERMISSIONS ||\n            error == SpeechRecognizer.ERROR_CLIENT ||\n\n[144 more lines in file. Use offset=138 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631317667}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e0752fb","parentId":"7493764c","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:06.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！当 `intent.resolveActivity()` 返回 null 时（小米设备上没有可用的语音识别 Activity），`buildFallbackIntent` 返回 null，然后 `errorMessage` 被设置为 \"系统里没有可用的语音识别界面\"。\n\n但是用户看到的错误消息是\"似乎出错了呢\"，这可能是另一个错误。让我看看错误消息是从哪里来的。\n\n等等，\"似乎出错了呢\" 这个中文消息不在代码里。让我搜索一下。","thinkingSignature":"386b05967f028b44dba74dc69105b88223b1f280c2e238a43823563f6b81f75b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jgohy1u1a402_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\ngrep -rn \"似乎\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":84503,"output":187,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631317682}}
