{"type":"message","id":"d8424c65","parentId":"0d28b755","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:25.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有找到。那\"似乎出错了呢\"可能是用户看到的系统弹窗消息，或者是用户对错误信息的描述。\n\n让我重新思考整个问题：1. 用户点击跟读题目\n2. 授予麦克风权限3. 弹窗提示错误\n\n可能的问题：- 工厂方法返回了错误的引擎- 引擎初始化失败- startPractice 失败- buildFallbackIntent 失败\n\n最可能的根本问题是：**小米设备上没有可用的系统语音识别 Activity**。\n\n解决方案：- 不依赖 Activity 的语音识别- 使用 SpeechRecognizer（不需要 Activity）而不是 ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH（需要 Activity）让我看看 SpeechPracticeRecognizer 使用的是哪种方式。从代码看，ensureRecognizer() 创建的是 SpeechRecognizer，这是正确的。但 buildFallbackIntent 使用的是 ACTION_RECOGNIZE_SPEECH，需要 Activity。\n\n所以问题是：用户授予麦克风权限后，如果引擎初始化失败或 startPractice 失败，系统会尝试用 Activity 方式启动语音识别，但小米设备可能没有这个 Activity。\n\n让我确保即使没有可用的 fallback Activity，错误消息也是清晰的，并确保引擎能正常工作。\n\n实际上，我应该直接调试这个问题。但更好的方法是确保系统语音引擎能正常工作，不管设备上有没有语音识别 Activity。\n\n问题可能出在引擎的初始化上，需要检查 startPractice 中的设置是否正确，特别是麦克风权限和语音识别服务的可用性检测。","thinkingSignature":"e6550a34e1813c627ff20497857f6c563508f41874f57688227dd593cd5191e8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xud2as2nn97n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\ngrep -n \"isAvailable\\|ensureRecognizer\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":84881,"output":392,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631331752}}
{"type":"message","id":"03fdfd00","parentId":"d8424c65","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:25.986Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xud2as2nn97n_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"46:    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean = SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)\n65:        val available = if (isAvailable()) \"recognizer=available\" else \"recognizer=missing\"\n94:        if (!isAvailable()) {\n98:        ensureRecognizer()\n162:    private fun ensureRecognizer() {\n254:        return if (isAvailable()) {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"46:    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean = SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)\n65:        val available = if (isAvailable()) \"recognizer=available\" else \"recognizer=missing\"\n94:        if (!isAvailable()) {\n98:        ensureRecognizer()\n162:    private fun ensureRecognizer() {\n254:        return if (isAvailable()) {","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631345979}}
{"type":"message","id":"74b75c6f","parentId":"03fdfd00","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:33.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`isAvailable()` 检查 `SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)`。这应该返回 true 如果设备有语音识别能力。但问题可能是小米设备返回了 false。让我看看 startPractice 失败时设置的错误消息。从代码看，如果 isAvailable() 返回 false，错误消息是 \"未检测到系统语音识别服务，请检查系统语音输入/Google 语音识别是否可用\"。\n\n用户看到的消息是 \"似乎出错了呢\"，这可能是：\n1. 用户记错了实际错误消息2. 或者有另一个错误弹窗让我直接尝试一个更简单的解决方案：确保错误消息更清晰，并且如果系统语音不可用，给用户更好的提示。\n\n但更好的方法可能是：直接检查系统是否有语音识别能力，如果没有，给用户一个更友好的错误消息，而不是尝试回退。\n\n让我修改代码，确保：\n1. 错误消息更清晰2. 如果系统语音不可用，给出明确的提示3. 不依赖 fallback Activity","thinkingSignature":"301abf874368ad68c90c775eda468331ef70b91b5289a6a15fcee5b4ea959f4f"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下可能的问题根源，并做一个更彻底的修复。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9swqyqahsp3b_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","limit":20,"offset":44}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":85367,"output":279,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631345989}}
{"type":"message","id":"1eed6f98","parentId":"74b75c6f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:33.694Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9swqyqahsp3b_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    private var currentAttemptId: Int = 0\n\n    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean = SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)\n\n    private fun hasMicPermission(): Boolean {\n        return ContextCompat.checkSelfPermission(context, Manifest.permission.RECORD_AUDIO) == PackageManager.PERMISSION_GRANTED\n    }\n\n    private fun recognitionServicePackages(): List<String> {\n        val intent = Intent(RecognitionService.SERVICE_INTERFACE)\n        val services = if (Build.VERSION.SDK_INT >= Build.VERSION_CODES.TIRAMISU) {\n            context.packageManager.queryIntentServices(intent, PackageManager.ResolveInfoFlags.of(0))\n        } else {\n            @Suppress(\"DEPRECATION\")\n            context.packageManager.queryIntentServices(intent, 0)\n        }\n        return services.mapNotNull { it.serviceInfo?.packageName }.distinct().sorted()\n    }\n\n    private fun debugSummary(): String {\n\n[218 more lines in file. Use offset=64 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631353684}}
{"type":"message","id":"9769a6f8","parentId":"1eed6f98","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:22:42.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！`SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)` 可能返回 false，尤其是在小米设备上，即使系统有语音识别功能。这个方法检查的是设备上是否安装了语音识别服务。但小米设备可能没有预装 Google 语音识别，或者系统语音识别服务被定制了。解决方案：\n1. 不依赖 `isRecognitionAvailable()` 的返回值来决定是否使用语音识别\n2. 直接尝试创建 SpeechRecognizer，如果失败再处理\n3. 改进错误处理让我修改 `startPractice` 方法，让它更健壮。","thinkingSignature":"b4765486d153fb316f75ca6fff864242b9f8a5dfd00e72e35e5d883865a82e3e"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现问题了。小米设备上 `SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable()` 可能返回 false，导致整个语音识别被禁用。\n\n让我做一个更彻底的修复 - 让系统语音引擎在小米设备上也能尝试工作：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qv44le8g1qu2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeRecognizer.kt","newText":"    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean {\n        // 尝试检查是否有语音识别服务，但即使没有也尝试创建 recognizer\n        // 因为某些设备上这个方法返回 false 但实际可以使用\n        return true // 总是尝试，让 create 时处理具体错误\n    }","oldText":"    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean = SpeechRecognizer.isRecognitionAvailable(context)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":85859,"output":300,"cacheRead":22326,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631353698}}
