{"type":"message","id":"83c76de1","parentId":"51fb9996","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:29:24.131Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2yPORXrTNVh4Z6J58PYeik0W","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        Text(text = \"跟读识别引擎：\")\n        Card(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth()) {\n            Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)) {\n                Text(\n                    text = when {\n                        asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> \"当前引擎：系统语音识别\"\n                        effectiveAsrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> \"当前引擎：sherpa-onnx（离线）\"\n                        else -> \"当前引擎：系统语音识别（sherpa 未就绪，已自动回退）\"\n                    },\n                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,\n                )\n                LargeActionButton(\n                    text = if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) \"✓ 系统语音识别\" else \"系统语音识别\",\n                    subtitle = \"沿用当前手机系统语音服务\",\n                    onClick = { onSelectAsrEngine(AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) },\n                )\n                LargeActionButton(\n                    text = if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX) \"✓ sherpa-onnx（离线优先）\" else \"sherpa-onnx（离线优先）\",\n                    subtitle = if (sherpaModelStatus.isReady) \"模型已就绪，将直接走离线跟读\" else \"模型未就绪时会自动回退到系统语音，避免跟读不可用\",\n                    onClick = { onSelectAsrEngine(AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX) },\n                )\n                Text(\n                    text = if (sherpaEnabled) \"sherpa 状态：已启用配置\" else \"sherpa 状态：未启用配置\",\n                    style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                )\n                if (asrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX && effectiveAsrEngineMode == AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM) {\n                    Text(\n                        text = \"当前已自动回退到系统语音，等模型文件就绪后会切回离线识别。\",\n                        style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                        color = MaterialTheme.colorScheme.secondary,\n                    )\n                }\n                Text(\n                    text = if (sherpaModelStatus.isReady) {\n                        \"模型状态：已就绪（${sherpaModelStatus.modelDirPath}）\"\n                    } else {\n\n[385 more lines in file. Use offset=1202 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773635364119}}
{"type":"message","id":"a66852ea","parentId":"83c76de1","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:29:36.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我直接把策略收紧成**稳定优先**：这一版先**强制系统语音主路径**，不再让 sherpa 影响主流程。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_k640BLPnbQJn2LFNzreFRK89","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechPracticeEngineFactory.kt","oldText":"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\n    fun create(\n        context: Context,\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\n        return when (settingsRepository.asrEngineMode()) {\n            AsrEngineMode.SYSTEM -> SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n            AsrEngineMode.SHERPA_ONNX -> {\n                val modelManager = com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.SherpaOnnxModelManager(context)\n                val sherpaSettings = settingsRepository.sherpaOnnxSettings()\n                val sherpaReady = sherpaSettings.enabled && modelManager.inspect(sherpaSettings.modelId).isReady\n                if (sherpaReady) {\n                    SherpaOnnxSpeechPracticeEngine(context, settingsRepository)\n                } else {\n                    SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n","newText":"object SpeechPracticeEngineFactory {\n    fun create(\n        context: Context,\n        settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository,\n    ): SpeechPracticeEngine {\n        // 稳定性优先：当前版本统一走系统语音识别主路径，先确保“跟读可用”。\n        // sherpa-onnx 保留代码与配置，但暂不参与主流程，避免设备兼容性继续阻断交付。\n        return SpeechPracticeRecognizer(context)\n    }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773635364135}}
