{"type":"message","id":"167e8875","parentId":"2363abec","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:58:47.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring model assets**\n\nIt seems like the documentation suggests that sherpa models might not be ready yet, but I wonder if the model assets might actually exist now. I should search for ONNX files in the project. Earlier, I found some libraries, but no model files. Maybe it’s a good idea to check the assets for those sherpa models and see what’s available for inspection. Let's dig deeper to find out!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我先查一下：**本地 sherpa 模型文件到底有没有跟着包走**。如果模型其实已经在包里，我可以直接把默认跟读切到离线本地，不用等云端 ASR。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Vd5mt0ZHdv00NSGVx9fH2enI","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app\nprintf '=== sherpa model assets in source ===\\n'\nfind app/src/main -type f \\( -name '*.onnx' -o -name 'tokens.txt' \\) | sed -n '1,120p'\nprintf '\\n=== sherpa model assets in built apk ===\\n'\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport zipfile, os\napk='app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk'\nif os.path.exists(apk):\n    with zipfile.ZipFile(apk) as z:\n        hits=[i.filename for i in z.infolist() if i.filename.endswith('.onnx') or i.filename.endswith('tokens.txt')]\n        for h in hits[:200]: print(h)\n        print('COUNT', len(hits))\nPY\n","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773637101943}}
