{"type":"message","id":"94b81b50","parentId":"0b45f909","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:01:48.987Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_kVSOqSVvAcwDvDNU5RFLANip","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# sherpa-onnx 模型目录约定\n\n更新日期：2026-03-15\n\n## 默认模型根目录\n\nApp 私有目录：\n- `<filesDir>/sherpa-onnx/`\n\n## 当前默认模型 ID\n\n- `english-zipformer-small`\n\n## 目录结构约定\n\n```text\n<filesDir>/sherpa-onnx/\n  english-zipformer-small/\n    tokens.txt\n    encoder.onnx\n    decoder.onnx\n    joiner.onnx\n```\n\n## 第一阶段说明\n\n当前先把：\n- 模型目录\n- 必要文件检查\n- 未就绪提示\n\n做成固定结构。\n\n后续真的接入 sherpa-onnx 时，再把：\n- 模型下载/导入\n- 初始化加载\n- 录音推理\n\n接进去。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773637308979}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab456bc4","parentId":"94b81b50","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:01:48.997Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_z0xhnPHUlEaH2e1djYBVuXq9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 少儿英语练习册｜sherpa-onnx 接入方案\n\n更新日期：2026-03-15\n状态：已选型，待实施\n\n## 一、为什么选 sherpa-onnx\n\n已确认当前手机端系统语音链路会落到：\n- `com.xiaomi.mibrain.speech`\n\n并且在跟读场景下持续报错，因此继续依赖系统 `SpeechRecognizer` 已经不稳。\n\n`sherpa-onnx` 的价值在于：\n- **离线运行**，不需要联网\n- **Android/Kotlin 可接入**\n- 支持 **本地语音识别**\n- 可绕开厂商系统语音服务\n- 无 API 费用\n\n根据官方资料，sherpa-onnx：\n- 支持 Android\n- 支持 Kotlin / Java\n- 支持本地实时语音识别\n\n## 二、当前项目推荐落地方式\n\n### 目标\n在当前 app 中新增一条不依赖系统语音服务的识别引擎：\n- `SYSTEM`：现有系统语音识别（保留）\n- `SHERPA_ONNX`：新增本地离线识别\n\n### 推荐模型方向\n当前 app 主要是 **儿童英语跟读**，优先考虑：\n- 英语模型\n- 体积较小\n- Android 端可跑\n\n第一阶段建议：\n- 先用 **英语小模型** 跑通闭环\n- 先求“能稳定识别并接评分”，再优化效果\n\n## 三、实施拆分\n\n### Phase 1：设置与引擎抽象\n- 新增 `AsrEngineMode`\n- 在设置里保存当前识别引擎\n- 为后续 `SHERPA_ONNX` 接入预留配置位\n\n### Phase 2：接入 sherpa-onnx 依赖与模型资产\n- 引入 Android 可用依赖\n- 增加模型文件存放与加载逻辑\n- 设计首次启动的模型检查逻辑\n\n### Phase 3：录音与推理链路\n- App 本地采集音频\n- 把音频帧送进 sherpa-onnx\n- 产出识别文本\n\n### Phase 4：接现有评分逻辑\n- 把识别文本喂给 `ReadAlongScorer`\n- 保留现有星级、鼓励语、逐词反馈\n\n### Phase 5：模式切换与降级\n- 设置页可切换 `SYSTEM / SHERPA_ONNX`\n- 如果模型未就绪，明确提示，不静默失败\n\n## 四、验收标准\n\n第一阶段验收不追求最优识别率，只追求：\n1. 手机端不再依赖系统语音弹窗\n2. 能本地录音\n3. 能返回一段英语识别文本\n4. 能进入现有打分页面\n\n## 五、当前推进结论\n\n本轮已确认：\n- 免费路线选择：`sherpa-onnx`\n- 技术路线：**本地离线识别优先**\n- 后续工作重点：从“修系统语音”切换到“接本地 ASR 引擎”\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773637308987}}
{"type":"message","id":"61ca1988","parentId":"ab456bc4","timestamp":"2026-03-16T05:01:49.003Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_qMrCPK9Y3qpWIxu1MOkqEDPD","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport java.io.File\n\nclass SherpaOnnxModelManager(context: Context) {\n    private val appContext = context.applicationContext\n\n    fun defaultModelId(): String = \"english-zipformer-small\"\n\n    fun canonicalModelId(modelId: String): String {\n        return when (modelId.trim()) {\n            \"\", \"english-small\" -> defaultModelId()\n            else -> modelId.trim()\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun modelsRootDir(): File {\n        return File(appContext.filesDir, \"sherpa-onnx\")\n    }\n\n    fun ensureModelsRootDir(): File {\n        return modelsRootDir().apply { mkdirs() }\n    }\n\n    fun modelDir(modelId: String): File {\n        return File(ensureModelsRootDir(), canonicalModelId(modelId))\n    }\n\n    fun ensureModelDir(modelId: String): File {\n        return modelDir(modelId).apply { mkdirs() }\n    }\n\n    fun requiredFiles(modelId: String): List<String> {\n        return when (canonicalModelId(modelId)) {\n            defaultModelId() -> listOf(\n                \"tokens.txt\",\n                \"encoder.onnx\",\n                \"decoder.onnx\",\n                \"joiner.onnx\",\n            )\n            else -> listOf(\n                \"tokens.txt\",\n                \"encoder.onnx\",\n                \"decoder.onnx\",\n                \"joiner.onnx\",\n            )\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun seedBundledModelIfAvailable(modelId: String): Boolean {\n        val canonicalId = canonicalModelId(modelId)\n        val targetDir = ensureModelDir(canonicalId)\n        val required = requiredFiles(canonicalId)\n        val assetPrefix = \"sherpa-onnx/$canonicalId\"\n        var copiedAny = false\n\n        required.forEach { fileName ->\n            val targetFile = File(targetDir, fileName)\n            if (targetFile.isFile) return@forEach\n            val assetPath = \"$assetPrefix/$fileName\"\n            val opened = runCatching { appContext.assets.open(assetPath) }.getOrNull() ?: return@forEach\n            opened.use { input ->\n                targetFile.outputStream().use { output -> input.copyTo(output) }\n            }\n            copiedAny = true\n        }\n\n        return copiedAny\n    }\n\n    fun inspect(modelId: String): SherpaOnnxModelStatus {\n        val canonicalId = canonicalModelId(modelId)\n        val dir = ensureModelDir(canonicalId)\n        val required = requiredFiles(canonicalId)\n        val missing = required.filterNot { File(dir, it).isFile }\n        return SherpaOnnxModelStatus(\n            modelId = canonicalId,\n            modelDirPath = dir.absolutePath,\n            requiredFiles = required,\n            missingFiles = missing,\n        )\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773637308997}}
