\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/path\\u003e\\u003c/svg\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\n\\u003cblockquote\\u003e\\n\\u003cp dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003eSmart glasses OS, with dozens of built-in apps. Users get AI assistant, notifications,\\ntranslation, screen mirror, captions, and more. Devs get to write 1 app that runs on\\nany pair of smart glasses.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003c/blockquote\\u003e\\n\\u003cp dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003eIt uses sherpa-onnx for real-time speech recognition on iOS and Android devices.\\nSee also \\u003ca class=\\\"issue-link js-issue-link\\\" data-error-text=\\\"Failed to load title\\\" data-id=\\\"3271084415\\\" data-permission-text=\\\"Title is private\\\" data-url=\\\"https://github.com/Mentra-Community/MentraOS/issues/861\\\" data-hovercard-type=\\\"pull_request\\\" data-hovercard-url=\\\"/Mentra-Community/MentraOS/pull/861/hovercard\\\" href=\\\"https://github.com/Mentra-Community/MentraOS/pull/861\\\"\\u003eMentra-Community/MentraOS#861\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003eIt uses Swift for iOS and Java for Android.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv class=\\\"markdown-heading\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003e\\u003ch3 tabindex=\\\"-1\\\" class=\\\"heading-element\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/SamYuan1990/flet_sherpa_onnx\\\"\\u003eflet_sherpa_onnx\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\u003ca id=\\\"user-content-flet_sherpa_onnx\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" aria-label=\\\"Permalink: flet_sherpa_onnx\\\" href=\\\"#flet_sherpa_onnx\\\"\\u003e\\u003csvg class=\\\"octicon octicon-link\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 16 16\\\" version=\\\"1.1\\\" width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"\\u003e\\u003cpath d=\\\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/path\\u003e\\u003c/svg\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\n\\u003cp dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003eFlet ASR/STT component based on sherpa-onnx.\\nExample \\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/SamYuan1990/i18n-agent-action\\\"\\u003ea chat box agent\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cdiv class=\\\"markdown-heading\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003e\\u003ch3 tabindex=\\\"-1\\\" class=\\\"heading-element\\\" dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003e\\u003ca href=\\\"https://github.com/ai-bot-pro/achatbot-go\\\"\\u003eachatbot-go\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/h3\\u003e\\u003ca id=\\\"user-content-achatbot-go\\\" class=\\\"anchor\\\" aria-label=\\\"Permalink: achatbot-go\\\" href=\\\"#achatbot-go\\\"\\u003e\\u003csvg class=\\\"octicon octicon-link\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 16 16\\\" version=\\\"1.1\\\" width=\\\"16\\\" height=\\\"16\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\"\\u003e\\u003cpath d=\\\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\\\"\\u003e\\u003c/path\\u003e\\u003c/svg\\u003e\\u003c/a\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\n\\u003cp dir=\\\"auto\\\"\\u003ea multimodal chatbot based on go with sherpa-onnx's speech lib api.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003c/article\\u003e\",\"loaded\":true,\"timedOut\":false,\"errorMessage\":null,\"headerInfo\":{\"toc\":[{\"level\":3,\"text\":\"Supported functions\",\"anchor\":\"suppor