: \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 14:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b544e7bd0b4b0c3a57aa6226766c]\nou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7: 以下内容来自trae：我已经帮你解决了 GPT 没能搞定的本地离线跟读问题。现在，你的 App 已经 内置了完整的离线语音识别能力 ，不再依赖小米系统服务或任何网络。\n\n### 执行过程\n1. 模型下载与集成 ：\n   - 我找到了 sherpa-onnx 官方提供的英文 zipformer 模型。\n   - 通过 wget 和 tar 命令，将模型文件下载并解压到了 App 的 assets 目录中：\n     - 路径 ： app/src/main/assets/sherpa-onnx/english-zipformer-small/\n     - 文件 ： tokens.txt , encoder-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx , decoder-epoch-99-avg-1.onnx , joiner-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx\n2. 代码适配与修复 ：\n   - 模型路径修正 ：更新了 SherpaOnnxModelManager.kt 和 SherpaOnnxRuntime.kt ，确保代码能准确加载 .int8 量化版本的模型文件名。\n   - 清理与整合 ：清理了下载过程中的临时文件，确保 assets 目录干净、规范。\n### 当前状态\n- 本地离线跟读功能已闭环 ：所有必需的模型文件都已正确集成到你的 APK 中。\n- 稳定性 ：此方案不依赖任何外部服务，只要麦克风权限正常，跟读功能就能稳定运行。\n你现在可以重新编译 App。如果之前的小米系统语音服务仍然报错，请在 App 设置中将跟读引擎切换为 Sherpa-Onnx (离线跟读) ，即可体验完全在本地运行的跟读打分功能。"}],"timestamp":1773642582221}}
{"type":"message","id":"9734c7e5","parentId":"78186ccf","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:30:03.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Verifying code and artifacts**\n\nI need to respond by verifying the code and artifacts, maybe by building the APK and reporting on it. It's important not to make assumptions, so I should inspect assets, the model manager, runtime, and filename mapping because the APK should include the model count. If it hasn’t been committed yet, I will need to do that. I must also mention if the actual issue is fixed on the device after verification. Let's proceed with the reads/exec.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我先不把这段话当成“已修好”，先按验收口径核：**模型文件是否真的进了 assets、代码是否匹配 `.int8` 文件名、APK 里是否已带模型。**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ARZFa1TPLOseNJq2cDeoHA1h","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/data/SherpaOnnxModelManager.kt","offset":1,"limit":220}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yugLGb1Rs0bYrSTAgjktorXO","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SherpaOnnxRuntime.kt","offset":1,"limit":260}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_jHQERdUFJLLTl3bv1uuLOqXI","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app\nprintf '=== source model assets ===\\n'\nfind app/src/main/assets/sherpa-onnx -type f 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,120p'\nprintf '\\n=== count model files in source ===\\n'\nfind app/src/main/assets/sherpa-onnx -type f \\( -name '*.onnx' -o -name 'tokens.txt' \\) 2>/dev/null | wc -l\nprintf '\\n=== verify model filenames in source ===\\n'\nfind app/src/main/assets/sherpa-onnx/english-zipformer-small -maxdepth 1 -type f 2>/dev/null | xargs -I{} basename '{}' | sort\nprintf '\\n=== model files in latest apk ===\\n'\npython3 - <<'PY'\nimport zipfile, os\napk='app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk'\nif os.path.exists(apk):\n    with zipfile.ZipFile(apk) as z:\n        hits=[i.filename for i in z.infolist() if i.filename.startswith('assets/sherpa-onnx/') and (i.filename.endswith('.onnx') or i.filename.endswith('tokens.txt'))]\n        for h in hits: print(h)\n        print('COUNT', len(hits))\nelse:\n    print('NO_APK')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773642582224}}
{"type":"message","id":"ed606f09","parentId":"9734c7e5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:30:03.232Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ARZFa1TPLOseNJq2cDeoHA1h","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport java.io.File\n\nclass SherpaOnnxModelManager(context: Context) {\n    private val appContext = context.applicationContext\n\n    fun defaultModelId(): String = \"english-zipformer-small\"\n\n    fun canonicalModelId(modelId: String): String {\n        return when (modelId.trim()) {\n            \"\", \"english-small\" -> defaultModelId()\n            else -> modelId.trim()\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun modelsRootDir(): File {\n        return File(appContext.filesDir, \"sherpa-onnx\")\n    }\n\n    fun ensureModelsRootDir(): File {\n        return modelsRootDir().apply { mkdirs() }\n    }\n\n    fun modelDir(modelId: String): File {\n        return File(ensureModelsRootDir(), canonicalModelId(modelId))\n    }\n\n    fun ensureModelDir(modelId: String): File {\n        return modelDir(modelId).apply { mkdirs() }\n    }\n\n    fun requiredFiles(modelId: String): List<String> {\n        return when (canonicalModelId(modelId)) {\n            defaultModelId() -> listOf(\n                \"tokens.txt\",\n                \"encoder-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx\",\n                \"decoder-epoch-99-avg-1.onnx\",\n                \"joiner-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx\",\n            )\n            else -> listOf(\n                \"tokens.txt\",\n                \"encoder.onnx\",\n                \"decoder.onnx\",\n                \"joiner.onnx\",\n            )\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun seedBundledModelIfAvailable(modelId: String): Boolean {\n        val canonicalId = canonicalModelId(modelId)\n        val targetDir = ensureModelDir(canonicalId)\n        val required = requiredFiles(canonicalId)\n        val assetPrefix = \"sherpa-onnx/$canonicalId\"\n        var copiedAny = false\n\n        required.forEach { fileName ->\n            val targetFile = File(targetDir, fileName)\n            if (targetFile.isFile) return@forEach\n            val assetPath = \"$assetPrefix/$fileName\"\n            val opened = runCatching { appContext.assets.open(assetPath) }.getOrNull() ?: return@forEach\n            opened.use { input ->\n                targetFile.outputStream().use { output -> input.copyTo(output) }\n            }\n            copiedAny = true\n        }\n\n        return copiedAny\n    }\n\n    fun inspect(modelId: String): SherpaOnnxModelStatus {\n        val canonicalId = canonicalModelId(modelId)\n        val dir = ensureModelDir(canonicalId)\n        val required = requiredFiles(canonicalId)\n        val missing = required.filterNot { File(dir, it).isFile }\n        return SherpaOnnxModelStatus(\n            modelId = canonicalId,\n            modelDirPath = dir.absolutePath,\n            requiredFiles = required,\n            missingFiles = missing,\n        )\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642603224}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0d2836b","parentId":"ed606f09","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:30:03.239Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_yugLGb1Rs0bYrSTAgjktorXO","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx.FeatureConfig\nimport com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx.OfflineModelConfig\nimport com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx.OfflineRecognizer\nimport com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx.OfflineRecognizerConfig\nimport com.k2fsa.sherpa.onnx.OfflineTransducerModelConfig\nimport com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.SherpaOnnxModelStatus\nimport java.io.File\n\nclass SherpaOnnxRuntime(\n    context: Context,\n    private val modelStatus: SherpaOnnxModelStatus,\n    private val sampleRate: Int = 16_000,\n    private val featureDim: Int = 80,\n    private val numThreads: Int = 2,\n) {\n    private val appContext = context.applicationContext\n\n    var recognizer: OfflineRecognizer? = null\n        private set\n\n    fun isModelReady(): Boolean = modelStatus.isReady\n\n    fun recognizerClassName(): String = OfflineRecognizer::class.java.name\n\n    fun initialize(): Boolean {\n        if (!modelStatus.isReady) {\n            shutdown()\n            return false\n        }\n        if (recognizer != null) return true\n\n        val modelDir = File(modelStatus.modelDirPath)\n        val encoder = File(modelDir, \"encoder-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx\")\n        val decoder = File(modelDir, \"decoder-epoch-99-avg-1.onnx\")\n        val joiner = File(modelDir, \"joiner-epoch-99-avg-1.int8.onnx\")\n        val tokens = File(modelDir, \"tokens.txt\")\n        if (!encoder.isFile || !decoder.isFile || !joiner.isFile || !tokens.isFile) {\n            shutdown()\n            return false\n        }\n\n        val transducer = OfflineTransducerModelConfig().apply {\n            this.encoder = encoder.absolutePath\n            this.decoder = decoder.absolutePath\n            this.joiner = joiner.absolutePath\n        }\n        val modelConfig = OfflineModelConfig().apply {\n            this.transducer = transducer\n            this.tokens = tokens.absolutePath\n            this.numThreads = numThreads\n            this.provider = \"cpu\"\n            this.debug = false\n        }\n        val featureConfig = FeatureConfig().apply {\n            this.sampleRate = sampleRate\n            this.featureDim = featureDim\n            this.dither = 0f\n        }\n        val recognizerConfig = OfflineRecognizerConfig().apply {\n            this.featConfig = featureConfig\n            this.modelConfig = modelConfig\n            this.decodingMethod = \"greedy_search\"\n            this.maxActivePaths = 4\n            this.blankPenalty = 0f\n        }\n\n        recognizer = OfflineRecognizer(appContext.assets, recognizerConfig)\n        return true\n    }\n\n    fun recognize(samples: ShortArray): String {\n        if (samples.isEmpty()) return \"\"\n        check(initialize()) { \"sherpa-onnx 模型未就绪\" }\n        val offlineRecognizer = recognizer ?: error(\"sherpa-onnx recognizer 初始化失败\")\n        val stream = offlineRecognizer.createStream()\n        return try {\n            stream.acceptWaveform(samples.toFloatPcm(), sampleRate)\n            offlineRecognizer.decode(stream)\n            offlineRecognizer.getResult(stream).text.orEmpty().trim()\n        } finally {\n            stream.release()\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun shutdown() {\n        runCatching { recognizer?.release() }\n        recognizer = null\n    }\n\n    private fun ShortArray.toFloatPcm(): FloatArray {\n        return FloatArray(size) { index ->\n            (this[index] / 32768.0f).coerceIn(-1f, 1f)\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642603232}}
