{"type":"message","id":"83c1c0b7","parentId":"71a72c02","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:14.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Checking for compile errors**\n\nI need to address a compile error that occurred, possibly due to previous changes in the scorer. I should inspect the KidsBoxTvApp around lines 1484 and examine the related data types. It’s also important to continue automatically, maybe using self-improvement? If there's an external compile failure, I might need to log that. I’ll read the relevant areas and look into the definitions of ReadAlongScorer and WordFeedback for clarity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"新产物还没出来，阻断原因我已经抓到了：**当前工作区本身有编译断点，不是讯飞配置这一步单独造成的。**  \n我先把这个断点补上，再继续出包。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_24Qt5VKhNma1NObJQRMro7E7","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt","offset":1468,"limit":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_GXKRXUbURKalT1JkSPjjVrVY","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/ReadAlongScorer.kt","offset":1,"limit":260}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_FtdX34zr6o3JWAIE9aLL8Com","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/data/WordFeedback.kt","offset":1,"limit":220}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773650759223}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6ae4902","parentId":"83c1c0b7","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:14.885Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_24Qt5VKhNma1NObJQRMro7E7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        return\n    }\n\n    FlowRow(\n        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),\n        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp),\n        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp),\n    ) {\n        words.forEach { word ->\n            val (containerColor, contentColor) = when (word.status) {\n                WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primaryContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onPrimaryContainer\n                WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.errorContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onErrorContainer\n                WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> Color(0xFFFFE0B2) to Color(0xFF7A4A00)\n            }\n            Surface(color = containerColor, contentColor = contentColor, shape = MaterialTheme.shapes.small) {\n                Text(\n                    text = when (word.status) {\n                        WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> word.word\n                        WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> \"× ${word.word}\"\n                        WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> \"+ ${word.word}\"\n                    },\n                    modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 10.dp, vertical = 6.dp),\n                    style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodySmall,\n                )\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun ResultScreen(\n    bookTitle: String,\n    mode: QuizMode,\n    unitTitle: String,\n    result: SessionResult,\n    sessionWrongCount: Int,\n    gainedStars: Int,\n    practiceBonusStars: Int,\n    totalStars: Int,\n    totalWrongCount: Int,\n    newBadges: List<Badge>,\n    onBackHome: () -> Unit,\n    onRetry: () -> Unit,\n    onChooseUnit: () -> Unit,\n) {\n    val title = when (mode) {\n        QuizMode.WORD -> \"单词测验结果\"\n        QuizMode.SENTENCE -> \"句子测验结果\"\n        QuizMode.MIXED -> \"混合挑战结果\"\n        QuizMode.WRONG_REVIEW -> \"错题复习结果\"\n    }\n    val starText = when (gainedStars) {\n        3 -> \"★★★\"\n        2 -> \"★★\"\n        1 -> \"★\"\n        else -> \"0 星\"\n    }\n\n    Box(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize().padding(36.dp), contentAlignment = Alignment.Center) {\n        Card(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth()) {\n\n[45 more lines in file. Use offset=1528 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650774878}}
{"type":"message","id":"26835845","parentId":"f6ae4902","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:14.890Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_GXKRXUbURKalT1JkSPjjVrVY","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport kotlin.math.max\nimport kotlin.math.roundToInt\n\ndata class ReadAlongScore(\n    val totalScore: Int,\n    val accuracyScore: Int,\n    val fluencyScore: Int,\n    val integrityScore: Int,\n    val encouragementTitle: String,\n    val encouragementDetail: String,\n    val targetWordFeedback: List<WordFeedback>,\n)\n\ndata class WordFeedback(\n    val word: String,\n    val score: Int,\n    val isCorrect: Boolean,\n)\n\nobject ReadAlongScorer {\n    fun score(targetText: String, recognizedText: String): ReadAlongScore {\n        // This is a simplified scoring logic. A real implementation would use more sophisticated\n        // algorithms, like Levenshtein distance, to calculate scores and provide detailed feedback.\n        val targetWords = targetText.trim().split(\"\\\\s+\".toRegex())\n        val recognizedWords = recognizedText.trim().split(\"\\\\s+\".toRegex())\n\n        val matchedWords = targetWords.intersect(recognizedWords.toSet()).size\n        val accuracy = if (targetWords.isEmpty()) 0 else (matchedWords * 100 / targetWords.size)\n        \n        val totalScore = accuracy\n        val encouragementTitle = when {\n            totalScore >= 85 -> \"太棒了！\"\n            totalScore >= 70 -> \"不错哦！\"\n            else -> \"继续加油！\"\n        }\n\n        return ReadAlongScore(\n            totalScore = totalScore,\n            accuracyScore = accuracy,\n            fluencyScore = 100, // Fluency and integrity are not calculated in this simplified version\n            integrityScore = 100,\n            encouragementTitle = encouragementTitle,\n            encouragementDetail = \"你读对了 $matchedWords 个单词，共 ${targetWords.size} 个。\",\n            targetWordFeedback = targetWords.map { word ->\n                WordFeedback(\n                    word = word,\n                    score = if (recognizedWords.contains(word)) 100 else 0,\n                    isCorrect = recognizedWords.contains(word)\n                )\n            }\n        )\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650774885}}
