{"type":"message","id":"b61369b4","parentId":"1608f14b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:48.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Fixing compile issues**\n\nI need to fix a compile error by reintroducing the WordMatchStatus and status field, or maybe I should adjust the UI. The user didn't ask for anything specific right now, but I think we should continue and update later. It seems necessary to inspect the IFlytek engine expectations around line 325 and also check the Cloud engine. So, I’ll focus on reading those sections to get a clearer picture!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_RtL4vXUkCLBQ5RDVdDAKqke5","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/IFlytekSpeechPracticeEngine.kt","offset":280,"limit":120}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Ea5x5GrVhxw7bjopVAW90E7t","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/CloudSpeechPracticeEngine.kt","offset":1,"limit":220}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773650789731}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d484198","parentId":"b61369b4","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:48.474Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_RtL4vXUkCLBQ5RDVdDAKqke5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                val resultJsonString = String(Base64.decode(resultBase64, Base64.NO_WRAP), Charsets.UTF_8)\n\n                // Parse with Gson and data classes for type safety\n                val decodedPayload = gson.fromJson(resultJsonString, IFlytekDecodedPayload::class.java)\n                val result = decodedPayload.readWord ?: decodedPayload.readSentence\n\n                if (result == null) {\n                    scope.launch {\n                        statusMessage = \"评测结果解析失败：无法找到评分。\"\n                        isListening = false\n                    }\n                    webSocket?.close(1000, \"Done\")\n                    return\n                }\n\n                val totalScore = result.totalScore.toInt()\n                val accuracyScore = result.accuracyScore.toInt()\n                val fluencyScore = result.fluencyScore.toInt()\n                val integrityScore = result.integrityScore.toInt()\n\n                val wordFeedbackList = result.words?.map { word ->\n                    WordFeedback(\n                        word = word.content,\n                        score = word.totalScore.toInt(),\n                        isCorrect = word.totalScore >= 80.0 // Threshold for correctness\n                    )\n                } ?: emptyList()\n\n                scope.launch {\n                    statusMessage = \"评测完成！\"\n                    isListening = false\n\n                    val encouragementTitle = when {\n                        totalScore >= 85 -> \"太棒了！\"\n                        totalScore >= 70 -> \"不错哦！\"\n                        else -> \"继续加油！\"\n                    }\n\n                    val score = ReadAlongScore(\n                        totalScore = totalScore,\n                        accuracyScore = accuracyScore,\n                        fluencyScore = fluencyScore,\n                        integrityScore = integrityScore,\n                        encouragementTitle = encouragementTitle,\n                        encouragementDetail = \"总分: $totalScore, 准确度: $accuracyScore, 流利度: $fluencyScore\",\n                        targetWordFeedback = wordFeedbackList\n                    )\n\n                    lastResult = SpeechPracticeResult(\n                        attemptId = currentAttemptId,\n                        targetLabel = currentTargetLabel,\n                        targetRewardId = currentTargetRewardId,\n                        score = score,\n                    )\n                }\n                webSocket?.close(1000, \"Done\")\n            }\n        } catch (e: Exception) { // Catch broader exceptions from Gson parsing as well\n            scope.launch {\n                statusMessage = \"结果处理失败: ${e.message}\"\n                isListening = false\n            }\n            e.printStackTrace()\n            webSocket?.close(1011, \"Parsing error\")\n        }\n    }\n\n    // 鉴权 URL 生成\n    private fun getAuthUrl(hostUrl: String, apiKey: String, apiSecret: String): String {\n        val url = java.net.URL(hostUrl)\n        val date = SimpleDateFormat(\"EEE, dd MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss z\", Locale.US).apply {\n            timeZone = TimeZone.getTimeZone(\"GMT\")\n        }.format(Date())\n\n        val builder = StringBuilder(\"host: \").append(url.host).append(\"\\n\")\n            .append(\"date: \").append(date).append(\"\\n\")\n            .append(\"GET \").append(url.path).append(\" HTTP/1.1\")\n\n        val mac = Mac.getInstance(\"hmacsha256\")\n        val spec = SecretKeySpec(apiSecret.toByteArray(Charset.forName(\"UTF-8\")), \"hmacsha256\")\n        mac.init(spec)\n        val hexDigits = mac.doFinal(builder.toString().toByteArray(Charset.forName(\"UTF-8\")))\n        val sha = Base64.encodeToString(hexDigits, Base64.NO_WRAP)\n\n        val authorization = String.format(\n            \"api_key=\\\"%s\\\", algorithm=\\\"%s\\\", headers=\\\"%s\\\", signature=\\\"%s\\\"\",\n            apiKey, \"hmac-sha256\", \"host date request-line\", sha\n        )\n\n        val httpUrl = hostUrl.toHttpUrl().newBuilder()\n            .addQueryParameter(\"authorization\", Base64.encodeToString(authorization.toByteArray(Charset.forName(\"UTF-8\")), Base64.NO_WRAP))\n            .addQueryParameter(\"date\", date)\n            .addQueryParameter(\"host\", url.host)\n            .build()\n\n        return httpUrl.toString()\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): android.content.Intent? = null\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): android.content.Intent? = null\n    override fun handleFallbackResult(data: android.content.Intent?): Boolean = false\n    override fun handleFallbackCancelled() {}\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean = false\n    override fun reset() {\n        scope.coroutineContext.cancelChildren()\n        webSocket?.cancel()\n        isListening = false\n        statusMessage = \"点击开始跟读 (讯飞星火)\"\n        lastResult = null\n    }\n    override fun shutdown() {\n        scope.cancel()\n        webSocket?.close(1000, \"Shutdown\")\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650808462}}
{"type":"message","id":"4efd1fbe","parentId":"2d484198","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:46:48.482Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Ea5x5GrVhxw7bjopVAW90E7t","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.getValue\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.mutableStateOf\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.setValue\nimport com.openclaw.englishworkbook.data.AppSettingsRepository\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.*\nimport okhttp3.*\nimport okhttp3.MediaType.Companion.toMediaType\nimport okhttp3.RequestBody.Companion.toRequestBody\nimport org.json.JSONObject\nimport java.io.IOException\nimport java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit\n\nclass CloudSpeechPracticeEngine(\n    private val context: Context,\n    private val settingsRepository: AppSettingsRepository\n) : SpeechPracticeEngine {\n\n    private val scope = CoroutineScope(Dispatchers.Main + SupervisorJob())\n    private val client = OkHttpClient.Builder()\n        .connectTimeout(30, TimeUnit.SECONDS)\n        .readTimeout(30, TimeUnit.SECONDS)\n        .writeTimeout(30, TimeUnit.SECONDS)\n        .build()\n\n    override var isListening by mutableStateOf(false)\n        private set\n    override var statusMessage by mutableStateOf(\"点击开始云端跟读\")\n        private set\n    override var lastResult by mutableStateOf<SpeechPracticeResult?>(null)\n        private set\n    override var lastErrorCode by mutableStateOf(0)\n        private set\n    override var lastErrorAttemptId by mutableStateOf(0)\n        private set\n\n    private var currentTargetText: String = \"\"\n    private var currentTargetLabel: String = \"\"\n    private var currentTargetRewardId: String = \"\"\n    private var nextAttemptId: Int = 1\n    private var currentAttemptId: Int = 0\n\n    private val recorder = PcmAudioRecorder()\n\n    override fun isAvailable(): Boolean = true\n\n    override fun startPractice(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): Boolean {\n        val openai = settingsRepository.openaiSettings()\n        if (openai.apiKey.isBlank()) {\n            statusMessage = \"请先在设置中配置 OpenAI API Key\"\n            return false\n        }\n\n        currentTargetText = targetText.trim()\n        currentTargetLabel = targetLabel\n        currentTargetRewardId = targetRewardId.trim()\n        currentAttemptId = nextAttemptId++\n        \n        lastResult = null\n        lastErrorCode = 0\n        lastErrorAttemptId = 0\n\n        isListening = true\n        statusMessage = \"正在录音，请读出：$currentTargetText\"\n\n        scope.launch {\n            try {\n                // Record for a fixed duration (5 seconds)\n                val samples = withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {\n                    if (!recorder.prepare()) {\n                        println(\"KidsBox: Failed to prepare recorder\")\n                        return@withContext shortArrayOf()\n                    }\n                    if (!recorder.start()) {\n                        println(\"KidsBox: Failed to start recorder\")\n                        return@withContext shortArrayOf()\n                    }\n                    \n                    val allSamples = mutableListOf<Short>()\n                    val startTime = System.currentTimeMillis()\n                    while (System.currentTimeMillis() - startTime < 5000) {\n                        val chunk = recorder.readChunk()\n                        if (chunk.isNotEmpty()) {\n                            allSamples.addAll(chunk.toList())\n                        }\n                        delay(10)\n                    }\n                    recorder.stop()\n                    recorder.release()\n                    allSamples.toShortArray()\n                }\n\n                if (samples.isEmpty()) {\n                    statusMessage = \"未检测到录音数据\"\n                    isListening = false\n                    return@launch\n                }\n\n                statusMessage = \"正在上传云端分析...\"\n                val recognizedText = uploadToWhisper(samples, openai.apiKey, openai.baseUrl)\n                \n                if (recognizedText.isNullOrBlank()) {\n                    statusMessage = \"云端识别失败，请检查网络或 API Key\"\n                } else {\n                    val score = ReadAlongScorer.score(currentTargetText, recognizedText)\n                    lastResult = SpeechPracticeResult(\n                        attemptId = currentAttemptId,\n                        targetLabel = currentTargetLabel,\n                        targetRewardId = currentTargetRewardId,\n                        score = score,\n                    )\n                    statusMessage = \"${score.encouragementTitle}，${score.encouragementDetail}\"\n                }\n            } catch (e: Exception) {\n                statusMessage = \"发生错误: ${e.message}\"\n                e.printStackTrace()\n            } finally {\n                isListening = false\n            }\n        }\n\n        return true\n    }\n\n    private suspend fun uploadToWhisper(samples: ShortArray, apiKey: String, baseUrl: String): String? {\n        return withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {\n            val wavData = WavUtils.pcmToWav(samples, 16000)\n            \n            val requestBody = MultipartBody.Builder()\n                .setType(MultipartBody.FORM)\n                .addFormDataPart(\"model\", \"whisper-1\")\n                .addFormDataPart(\"language\", \"en\")\n                .addFormDataPart(\"file\", \"audio.wav\", \n                    wavData.toRequestBody(\"audio/wav\".toMediaType()))\n                .build()\n\n            val request = Request.Builder()\n                .url(\"$baseUrl/audio/transcriptions\")\n                .header(\"Authorization\", \"Bearer $apiKey\")\n                .post(requestBody)\n                .build()\n\n            try {\n                client.newCall(request).execute().use { response ->\n                    if (!response.isSuccessful) {\n                        println(\"Whisper API Error: ${response.code} ${response.message}\")\n                        return@withContext null\n                    }\n                    val json = response.body?.string() ?: return@withContext null\n                    JSONObject(json).optString(\"text\")\n                }\n            } catch (e: IOException) {\n                e.printStackTrace()\n                null\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    override fun buildFallbackIntent(targetText: String, targetLabel: String, targetRewardId: String): android.content.Intent? = null\n    override fun buildFallbackIntentForCurrentTarget(): android.content.Intent? = null\n    override fun handleFallbackResult(data: android.content.Intent?): Boolean = false\n    override fun handleFallbackCancelled() {}\n    override fun shouldAutoFallback(error: Int): Boolean = false\n    override fun reset() {\n        scope.coroutineContext.cancelChildren()\n        isListening = false\n        statusMessage = \"点击开始云端跟读\"\n        lastResult = null\n    }\n    override fun shutdown() {\n        scope.cancel()\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650808474}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4874f22","parentId":"4efd1fbe","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:47:17.463Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Fixing app issues**\n\nI need to look into the app change that the user referenced. They've now provided credentials and asked me to continue, so I need to show progress with evidence from recent work. We encountered a compilation issue due to a mismatch with ReadAlongScorer and WordMatchStatus. It's essential I focus on fixing these errors and consider building a new APK with the iflytek configuration externalized. I'll check the git history for the expected definitions for WordFeedback and WordMatchStatus. Let's dive into this!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我继续直接修，不停在说明上。当前新增阻断我已经抓到：**Trae 改坏了评分数据结构，导致 app 现在编译不过。**  \n我先把这个断点补平，恢复可打包状态。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_A9Vd74LqR7mXf1sa0SRJhZYF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nprintf '=== search WordMatchStatus definitions/history ===\\n'\ngrep -Rni \"enum class WordMatchStatus\\|data class WordFeedback\\|WordMatchStatus\" apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java | sed -n '1,240p'\nprintf '\\n=== git history for ReadAlongScorer ===\\n'\ngit log --oneline -- apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/ReadAlongScorer.kt | sed -n '1,20p'\nprintf '\\n=== previous committed ReadAlongScorer from HEAD~1? ===\\n'\ngit show HEAD~1:apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/ReadAlongScorer.kt | sed -n '1,220p' || true","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773650808485}}
{"type":"message","id":"0faa0eae","parentId":"b4874f22","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:47:17.633Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_A9Vd74LqR7mXf1sa0SRJhZYF","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== search WordMatchStatus definitions/history ===\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:63:import com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio.WordMatchStatus\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:690:                                .filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1266:    val practiceMissedWords = practiceResult?.score?.targetWordFeedback.orEmpty().filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1478:                WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primaryContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onPrimaryContainer\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1479:                WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.errorContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onErrorContainer\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1480:                WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> Color(0xFFFFE0B2) to Color(0xFF7A4A00)\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1485:                        WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> word.word\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1486:                        WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> \"× ${word.word}\"\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1487:                        WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> \"+ ${word.word}\"\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/ReadAlongScorer.kt:16:data class WordFeedback(\n\n=== git history for ReadAlongScorer ===\n4990788 feat(kids-box-tv-app): debrand public package id and theme\n62588d8 feat(kids-box-tv-app): improve read-along feedback and word highlighting\n2feaf96 feat(kids-box-tv-app): add read-along practice and scoring\n\n=== previous committed ReadAlongScorer from HEAD~1? ===\npackage com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport kotlin.math.max\nimport kotlin.math.roundToInt\n\nenum class WordMatchStatus {\n    MATCHED,\n    MISSED,\n    EXTRA,\n}\n\ndata class WordFeedback(\n    val word: String,\n    val status: WordMatchStatus,\n)\n\ndata class ReadAlongScore(\n    val score: Int,\n    val targetText: String,\n    val recognizedText: String,\n    val matchedWords: Int,\n    val targetWordCount: Int,\n    val recognizedWordCount: Int,\n    val exactMatch: Boolean,\n    val targetWordFeedback: List<WordFeedback>,\n    val recognizedWordFeedback: List<WordFeedback>,\n    val rewardStars: Int,\n    val encouragementTitle: String,\n    val encouragementDetail: String,\n)\n\nobject ReadAlongScorer {\n    fun score(targetText: String, recognizedText: String): ReadAlongScore {\n        val normalizedTarget = normalize(targetText)\n        val normalizedRecognized = normalize(recognizedText)\n\n        val targetWords = normalizedTarget.split(\" \").filter { it.isNotBlank() }\n        val recognizedWords = normalizedRecognized.split(\" \").filter { it.isNotBlank() }\n        val alignment = alignWords(targetWords, recognizedWords)\n\n        val matchedWords = alignment.matchedPairs.size\n        val recall = if (targetWords.isEmpty()) 0.0 else matchedWords.toDouble() / targetWords.size.toDouble()\n        val precision = if (recognizedWords.isEmpty()) 0.0 else matchedWords.toDouble() / recognizedWords.size.toDouble()\n        val charSimilarity = similarity(normalizedTarget, normalizedRecognized)\n        val exactMatch = normalizedTarget == normalizedRecognized && normalizedTarget.isNotBlank()\n\n        val rawScore = when {\n            exactMatch -> 100.0\n            normalizedRecognized.isBlank() -> 0.0\n            else -> recall * 60.0 + precision * 20.0 + charSimilarity * 20.0\n        }\n        val finalScore = rawScore.roundToInt().coerceIn(0, 100)\n        val rewardStars = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> 3\n            finalScore >= 80 -> 2\n            finalScore >= 60 -> 1\n            else -> 0\n        }\n        val encouragementTitle = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> \"太棒了\"\n            finalScore >= 80 -> \"很棒\"\n            finalScore >= 60 -> \"接近了\"\n            else -> \"再试一次\"\n        }\n        val encouragementDetail = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> \"这次几乎和标准答案一致。\"\n            finalScore >= 80 -> \"大部分都读对了，再稳一点会更好。\"\n            finalScore >= 60 -> \"已经比较接近，重点看看漏掉的词。\"\n            else -> \"先慢一点，把每个词读完整。\"\n        }\n\n        return ReadAlongScore(\n            score = finalScore,\n            targetText = targetText,\n            recognizedText = recognizedText,\n            matchedWords = matchedWords,\n            targetWordCount = targetWords.size,\n            recognizedWordCount = recognizedWords.size,\n            exactMatch = exactMatch,\n            targetWordFeedback = targetWords.mapIndexed { index, word ->\n                WordFeedback(word = word, status = if (index in alignment.matchedTargetIndexes) WordMatchStatus.MATCHED else WordMatchStatus.MISSED)\n            },\n            recognizedWordFeedback = recognizedWords.mapIndexed { index, word ->\n                WordFeedback(word = word, status = if (index in alignment.matchedRecognizedIndexes) WordMatchStatus.MATCHED else WordMatchStatus.EXTRA)\n            },\n            rewardStars = rewardStars,\n            encouragementTitle = encouragementTitle,\n            encouragementDetail = encouragementDetail,\n        )\n    }\n\n    private fun normalize(text: String): String {\n        return text\n            .lowercase()\n            .replace(\"'\", \"\")\n            .replace(Regex(\"[^a-z0-9 ]\"), \" \")\n            .replace(Regex(\"\\\\s+\"), \" \")\n            .trim()\n    }\n\n    private data class AlignmentResult(\n        val matchedPairs: List<Pair<Int, Int>>,\n        val matchedTargetIndexes: Set<Int>,\n        val matchedRecognizedIndexes: Set<Int>,\n    )\n\n    private fun alignWords(targetWords: List<String>, recognizedWords: List<String>): AlignmentResult {\n        if (targetWords.isEmpty() || recognizedWords.isEmpty()) {\n            return AlignmentResult(emptyList(), emptySet(), emptySet())\n        }\n\n        val dp = Array(targetWords.size + 1) { IntArray(recognizedWords.size + 1) }\n        for (i in targetWords.indices.reversed()) {\n            for (j in recognizedWords.indices.reversed()) {\n                dp[i][j] = if (targetWords[i] == recognizedWords[j]) {\n                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] + 1\n                } else {\n                    max(dp[i + 1][j], dp[i][j + 1])\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        var i = 0\n        var j = 0\n        val pairs = mutableListOf<Pair<Int, Int>>()\n        while (i < targetWords.size && j < recognizedWords.size) {\n            when {\n                targetWords[i] == recognizedWords[j] -> {\n                    pairs += i to j\n                    i += 1\n                    j += 1\n                }\n                dp[i + 1][j] >= dp[i][j + 1] -> i += 1\n                else -> j += 1\n            }\n        }\n\n        return AlignmentResult(\n            matchedPairs = pairs,\n            matchedTargetIndexes = pairs.map { it.first }.toSet(),\n            matchedRecognizedIndexes = pairs.map { it.second }.toSet(),\n        )\n    }\n\n    private fun similarity(a: String, b: String): Double {\n        if (a.isBlank() && b.isBlank()) return 1.0\n        val distance = levenshtein(a, b)\n        val base = max(a.length, b.length).coerceAtLeast(1)\n        return (1.0 - distance.toDouble() / base.toDouble()).coerceIn(0.0, 1.0)\n    }\n\n    private fun levenshtein(a: String, b: String): Int {\n        if (a == b) return 0\n        if (a.isEmpty()) return b.length\n        if (b.isEmpty()) return a.length\n\n        val previous = IntArray(b.length + 1) { it }\n        val current = IntArray(b.length + 1)\n\n        for (i in a.indices) {\n            current[0] = i + 1\n            for (j in b.indices) {\n                val cost = if (a[i] == b[j]) 0 else 1\n                current[j + 1] = minOf(\n                    current[j] + 1,\n                    previous[j + 1] + 1,\n                    previous[j] + cost,\n                )\n            }\n            for (k in previous.indices) {\n                previous[k] = current[k]\n            }\n        }\n\n        return previous[b.length]\n    }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":91,"aggregated":"=== search WordMatchStatus definitions/history ===\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:63:import com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio.WordMatchStatus\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:690:                                .filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1266:    val practiceMissedWords = practiceResult?.score?.targetWordFeedback.orEmpty().filter { it.status == WordMatchStatus.MISSED }\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1478:                WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.primaryContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onPrimaryContainer\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1479:                WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> MaterialTheme.colorScheme.errorContainer to MaterialTheme.colorScheme.onErrorContainer\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1480:                WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> Color(0xFFFFE0B2) to Color(0xFF7A4A00)\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1485:                        WordMatchStatus.MATCHED -> word.word\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1486:                        WordMatchStatus.MISSED -> \"× ${word.word}\"\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/ui/KidsBoxTvApp.kt:1487:                        WordMatchStatus.EXTRA -> \"+ ${word.word}\"\napps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/ReadAlongScorer.kt:16:data class WordFeedback(\n\n=== git history for ReadAlongScorer ===\n4990788 feat(kids-box-tv-app): debrand public package id and theme\n62588d8 feat(kids-box-tv-app): improve read-along feedback and word highlighting\n2feaf96 feat(kids-box-tv-app): add read-along practice and scoring\n\n=== previous committed ReadAlongScorer from HEAD~1? ===\npackage com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport kotlin.math.max\nimport kotlin.math.roundToInt\n\nenum class WordMatchStatus {\n    MATCHED,\n    MISSED,\n    EXTRA,\n}\n\ndata class WordFeedback(\n    val word: String,\n    val status: WordMatchStatus,\n)\n\ndata class ReadAlongScore(\n    val score: Int,\n    val targetText: String,\n    val recognizedText: String,\n    val matchedWords: Int,\n    val targetWordCount: Int,\n    val recognizedWordCount: Int,\n    val exactMatch: Boolean,\n    val targetWordFeedback: List<WordFeedback>,\n    val recognizedWordFeedback: List<WordFeedback>,\n    val rewardStars: Int,\n    val encouragementTitle: String,\n    val encouragementDetail: String,\n)\n\nobject ReadAlongScorer {\n    fun score(targetText: String, recognizedText: String): ReadAlongScore {\n        val normalizedTarget = normalize(targetText)\n        val normalizedRecognized = normalize(recognizedText)\n\n        val targetWords = normalizedTarget.split(\" \").filter { it.isNotBlank() }\n        val recognizedWords = normalizedRecognized.split(\" \").filter { it.isNotBlank() }\n        val alignment = alignWords(targetWords, recognizedWords)\n\n        val matchedWords = alignment.matchedPairs.size\n        val recall = if (targetWords.isEmpty()) 0.0 else matchedWords.toDouble() / targetWords.size.toDouble()\n        val precision = if (recognizedWords.isEmpty()) 0.0 else matchedWords.toDouble() / recognizedWords.size.toDouble()\n        val charSimilarity = similarity(normalizedTarget, normalizedRecognized)\n        val exactMatch = normalizedTarget == normalizedRecognized && normalizedTarget.isNotBlank()\n\n        val rawScore = when {\n            exactMatch -> 100.0\n            normalizedRecognized.isBlank() -> 0.0\n            else -> recall * 60.0 + precision * 20.0 + charSimilarity * 20.0\n        }\n        val finalScore = rawScore.roundToInt().coerceIn(0, 100)\n        val rewardStars = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> 3\n            finalScore >= 80 -> 2\n            finalScore >= 60 -> 1\n            else -> 0\n        }\n        val encouragementTitle = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> \"太棒了\"\n            finalScore >= 80 -> \"很棒\"\n            finalScore >= 60 -> \"接近了\"\n            else -> \"再试一次\"\n        }\n        val encouragementDetail = when {\n            finalScore >= 95 -> \"这次几乎和标准答案一致。\"\n            finalScore >= 80 -> \"大部分都读对了，再稳一点会更好。\"\n            finalScore >= 60 -> \"已经比较接近，重点看看漏掉的词。\"\n            else -> \"先慢一点，把每个词读完整。\"\n        }\n\n        return ReadAlongScore(\n            score = finalScore,\n            targetText = targetText,\n            recognizedText = recognizedText,\n            matchedWords = matchedWords,\n            targetWordCount = targetWords.size,\n            recognizedWordCount = recognizedWords.size,\n            exactMatch = exactMatch,\n            targetWordFeedback = targetWords.mapIndexed { index, word ->\n                WordFeedback(word = word, status = if (index in alignment.matchedTargetIndexes) WordMatchStatus.MATCHED else WordMatchStatus.MISSED)\n            },\n            recognizedWordFeedback = recognizedWords.mapIndexed { index, word ->\n                WordFeedback(word = word, status = if (index in alignment.matchedRecognizedIndexes) WordMatchStatus.MATCHED else WordMatchStatus.EXTRA)\n            },\n            rewardStars = rewardStars,\n            encouragementTitle = encouragementTitle,\n            encouragementDetail = encouragementDetail,\n        )\n    }\n\n    private fun normalize(text: String): String {\n        return text\n            .lowercase()\n            .replace(\"'\", \"\")\n            .replace(Regex(\"[^a-z0-9 ]\"), \" \")\n            .replace(Regex(\"\\\\s+\"), \" \")\n            .trim()\n    }\n\n    private data class AlignmentResult(\n        val matchedPairs: List<Pair<Int, Int>>,\n        val matchedTargetIndexes: Set<Int>,\n        val matchedRecognizedIndexes: Set<Int>,\n    )\n\n    private fun alignWords(targetWords: List<String>, recognizedWords: List<String>): AlignmentResult {\n        if (targetWords.isEmpty() || recognizedWords.isEmpty()) {\n            return AlignmentResult(emptyList(), emptySet(), emptySet())\n        }\n\n        val dp = Array(targetWords.size + 1) { IntArray(recognizedWords.size + 1) }\n        for (i in targetWords.indices.reversed()) {\n            for (j in recognizedWords.indices.reversed()) {\n                dp[i][j] = if (targetWords[i] == recognizedWords[j]) {\n                    dp[i + 1][j + 1] + 1\n                } else {\n                    max(dp[i + 1][j], dp[i][j + 1])\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        var i = 0\n        var j = 0\n        val pairs = mutableListOf<Pair<Int, Int>>()\n        while (i < targetWords.size && j < recognizedWords.size) {\n            when {\n                targetWords[i] == recognizedWords[j] -> {\n                    pairs += i to j\n                    i += 1\n                    j += 1\n                }\n                dp[i + 1][j] >= dp[i][j + 1] -> i += 1\n                else -> j += 1\n            }\n        }\n\n        return AlignmentResult(\n            matchedPairs = pairs,\n            matchedTargetIndexes = pairs.map { it.first }.toSet(),\n            matchedRecognizedIndexes = pairs.map { it.second }.toSet(),\n        )\n    }\n\n    private fun similarity(a: String, b: String): Double {\n        if (a.isBlank() && b.isBlank()) return 1.0\n        val distance = levenshtein(a, b)\n        val base = max(a.length, b.length).coerceAtLeast(1)\n        return (1.0 - distance.toDouble() / base.toDouble()).coerceIn(0.0, 1.0)\n    }\n\n    private fun levenshtein(a: String, b: String): Int {\n        if (a == b) return 0\n        if (a.isEmpty()) return b.length\n        if (b.isEmpty()) return a.length\n\n        val previous = IntArray(b.length + 1) { it }\n        val current = IntArray(b.length + 1)\n\n        for (i in a.indices) {\n            current[0] = i + 1\n            for (j in b.indices) {\n                val cost = if (a[i] == b[j]) 0 else 1\n                current[j + 1] = minOf(\n                    current[j] + 1,\n                    previous[j + 1] + 1,\n                    previous[j] + cost,\n                )\n            }\n            for (k in previous.indices) {\n                previous[k] = current[k]\n            }\n        }\n\n        return previous[b.length]\n    }\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773650837626}}
