{"type":"message","id":"592a3a46","parentId":"2df0e271","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:33.035Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring document access methods**\n\nI’m considering how to read the document. I could think about using a browser, but that might not be necessary. Instead, it seems simpler to fetch it via a web request using something like curl. Let’s see if using curl with the right URL can work. I’ll need to check the current application structure since it uses SpeechSpeaker and TtsSpeaker for “朗读.” I might explore adding IflytekTtsSpeaker through WebSocket or setting up a stub. I need to take a closer look at SpeechSpeaker and TtsSpeaker.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我继续直接推进：先把讯飞 **Smart TTS** 文档通过镜像读出来，再核当前 app 的朗读链路，决定把“机械音”替换到哪一层。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yde5Wzl5U9g9SBFjvwyIYlVI","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\ncurl -Lks 'https://r.jina.ai/http://https://www.xfyun.cn/doc/spark/smart-tts-android.html' | sed -n '1,260p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":120}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ZdTWhOMpQG0j0mjqL08WazUn","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/SpeechSpeaker.kt","offset":1,"limit":220}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_J1rStvjcAFaOqIioiuRJWT9H","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/kids-box-tv-app/app/src/main/java/com/openclaw/kidsboxtv/audio/TtsSpeaker.kt","offset":1,"limit":220}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652931499}}
{"type":"message","id":"f241d878","parentId":"592a3a46","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:34.115Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_yde5Wzl5U9g9SBFjvwyIYlVI","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Command still running (session tide-gulf, pid 12163). Use process (list/poll/log/write/kill/clear/remove) for follow-up."}],"details":{"status":"running","sessionId":"tide-gulf","pid":12163,"startedAt":1773652953092,"cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","tail":""},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773652954094}}
{"type":"message","id":"6be209ff","parentId":"f241d878","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:34.129Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ZdTWhOMpQG0j0mjqL08WazUn","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport android.media.AudioAttributes\nimport android.media.MediaPlayer\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.getValue\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.mutableStateOf\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.setValue\nimport org.json.JSONObject\nimport java.io.File\nimport java.security.MessageDigest\n\nclass SpeechSpeaker(context: Context) {\n    private val appContext = context.applicationContext\n    private val assetManager = appContext.assets\n    private val cacheDir = File(appContext.cacheDir, \"bundled-speech\")\n    private val fallbackTts = TtsSpeaker(appContext)\n    private val clipIndex: Map<String, String> = loadClipIndex()\n    private var mediaPlayer: MediaPlayer? = null\n    private var bundledStatusText by mutableStateOf(\n        if (clipIndex.isNotEmpty()) {\n            \"内置语音包已就绪（${clipIndex.size} 条）\"\n        } else {\n            \"未发现内置语音包，当前使用系统语音通道\"\n        }\n    )\n\n    fun speak(text: String): Boolean {\n        val normalized = text.trim()\n        if (normalized.isBlank()) return false\n\n        val bundledAssetPath = clipIndex[normalized]\n        if (bundledAssetPath != null) {\n            if (playBundledClip(bundledAssetPath)) {\n                bundledStatusText = \"内置语音包已就绪（${clipIndex.size} 条）\"\n                return true\n            }\n            bundledStatusText = \"内置语音播放失败，已尝试系统语音备用通道\"\n        }\n\n        val fallbackOk = fallbackTts.speak(normalized)\n        if (clipIndex.isNotEmpty()) {\n            bundledStatusText = when {\n                fallbackOk && bundledAssetPath == null -> \"内置语音缺少该片段，已切到系统语音备用通道\"\n                fallbackOk -> \"内置语音播放失败，已切到系统语音备用通道\"\n                bundledAssetPath == null -> \"内置语音缺少该片段，且系统语音备用通道不可用\"\n                else -> \"内置语音与系统语音都不可用\"\n            }\n        }\n        return fallbackOk\n    }\n\n    fun isReady(): Boolean = clipIndex.isNotEmpty() || fallbackTts.isReady()\n\n    fun hasBundledAudio(): Boolean = clipIndex.isNotEmpty()\n\n    fun getStatusMessage(): String = if (clipIndex.isNotEmpty()) bundledStatusText else fallbackTts.getStatusMessage()\n\n    fun shutdown() {\n        mediaPlayer?.runCatching {\n            stop()\n            release()\n        }\n        mediaPlayer = null\n        fallbackTts.shutdown()\n    }\n\n    private fun playBundledClip(assetPath: String): Boolean {\n        return runCatching {\n            val cachedFile = ensureCachedAsset(assetPath)\n            mediaPlayer?.release()\n            mediaPlayer = MediaPlayer().apply {\n                setAudioAttributes(\n                    AudioAttributes.Builder()\n                        .setUsage(AudioAttributes.USAGE_MEDIA)\n                        .setContentType(AudioAttributes.CONTENT_TYPE_SPEECH)\n                        .build()\n                )\n                setDataSource(cachedFile.absolutePath)\n                isLooping = false\n                prepare()\n                setOnCompletionListener { player ->\n                    player.release()\n                    if (mediaPlayer === player) {\n                        mediaPlayer = null\n                    }\n                }\n                setOnErrorListener { player, _, _ ->\n                    player.release()\n                    if (mediaPlayer === player) {\n                        mediaPlayer = null\n                    }\n                    false\n                }\n                start()\n            }\n            true\n        }.getOrElse {\n            false\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun ensureCachedAsset(assetPath: String): File {\n        cacheDir.mkdirs()\n        val extension = assetPath.substringAfterLast('.', \"m4a\")\n        val fileName = sha1(assetPath) + \".\" + extension\n        val cachedFile = File(cacheDir, fileName)\n        if (cachedFile.exists() && cachedFile.length() > 0) {\n            return cachedFile\n        }\n        assetManager.open(assetPath).use { input ->\n            cachedFile.outputStream().use { output ->\n                input.copyTo(output)\n            }\n        }\n        return cachedFile\n    }\n\n    private fun loadClipIndex(): Map<String, String> {\n        return runCatching {\n            val jsonText = assetManager.open(\"audio/en/index.json\").bufferedReader().use { it.readText() }\n            val jsonObject = JSONObject(jsonText)\n            buildMap {\n                val keys = jsonObject.keys()\n                while (keys.hasNext()) {\n                    val key = keys.next()\n                    put(key, jsonObject.getString(key))\n                }\n            }\n        }.getOrDefault(emptyMap())\n    }\n\n    private fun sha1(value: String): String {\n        val digest = MessageDigest.getInstance(\"SHA-1\").digest(value.toByteArray())\n        return digest.joinToString(separator = \"\") { byte -> \"%02x\".format(byte) }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773652954115}}
{"type":"message","id":"a25d5583","parentId":"6be209ff","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:34.151Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_J1rStvjcAFaOqIioiuRJWT9H","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"package com.openclaw.englishworkbook.audio\n\nimport android.content.Context\nimport android.media.AudioAttributes\nimport android.speech.tts.TextToSpeech\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.getValue\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.mutableStateOf\nimport androidx.compose.runtime.setValue\nimport java.util.Locale\n\nclass TtsSpeaker(context: Context) : TextToSpeech.OnInitListener {\n    private var pendingText: String? = null\n    private var initFinished: Boolean = false\n    private var readyState by mutableStateOf(false)\n    private var statusText by mutableStateOf(\"语音引擎初始化中\")\n\n    private val tts = TextToSpeech(context.applicationContext, this)\n\n    override fun onInit(status: Int) {\n        initFinished = true\n\n        if (status != TextToSpeech.SUCCESS) {\n            readyState = false\n            pendingText = null\n            statusText = buildInitFailureMessage()\n            return\n        }\n\n        tts.setAudioAttributes(\n            AudioAttributes.Builder()\n                .setUsage(AudioAttributes.USAGE_MEDIA)\n                .setContentType(AudioAttributes.CONTENT_TYPE_SPEECH)\n                .build()\n        )\n\n        val candidateLocales = listOf(Locale.US, Locale.UK, Locale.getDefault())\n        var languageReady = false\n        for (locale in candidateLocales) {\n            val result = tts.isLanguageAvailable(locale)\n            if (result >= TextToSpeech.LANG_AVAILABLE) {\n                tts.language = locale\n                languageReady = true\n                statusText = \"语音就绪：${locale.toLanguageTag()}\"\n                break\n            }\n        }\n\n        readyState = languageReady\n        if (!readyState) {\n            statusText = \"系统缺少可用英文语音包\"\n        }\n\n        pendingText?.let {\n            val queued = it\n            pendingText = null\n            speak(queued)\n        }\n    }\n\n    private fun buildInitFailureMessage(): String {\n        val installedEngines = runCatching { tts.engines }.getOrDefault(emptyList())\n        return when {\n            installedEngines.isEmpty() -> \"当前设备未安装系统语音引擎\"\n            else -> \"系统语音引擎启动失败，请切换默认 TTS 引擎或重启设备后重试\"\n        }\n    }\n\n    fun speak(text: String): Boolean {\n        if (text.isBlank()) return false\n        if (!initFinished) {\n            pendingText = text\n            statusText = \"语音引擎初始化中\"\n            return false\n        }\n        if (!readyState) {\n            return false\n        }\n        tts.stop()\n        val result = tts.speak(text, TextToSpeech.QUEUE_FLUSH, null, \"kids-box-tts\")\n        if (result != TextToSpeech.SUCCESS) {\n            statusText = \"语音播放失败，请检查系统 TTS 引擎\"\n            return false\n        }\n        return true\n    }\n\n    fun isReady(): Boolean = readyState\n\n    fun getStatusMessage(): String = statusText\n\n    fun shutdown() {\n        tts.stop()\n        tts.shutdown()\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773652954129}}
